 ('1', '1', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-17 13:25:01', '2016-10-17 13:25:01', '3c240ecc-bb38-4811-bf91-2de9fe57e0e2'),
 ('2', '2', 'en_us', 'Homepage', '<p>It’s true, this site doesn’t have a whole lot of content yet, but don’t worry. Our web developers have just installed the CMS, and they’re setting things up for the content editors this very moment. Soon Localhost will be an oasis of fresh perspectives, sharp analyses, and astute opinions that will keep you coming back again and again.</p>', 'Partner with proven entrepreneurs. Harness startup behaviors that complement what you’re doing already. And discover what else you could be doing.', 'We created Startupbootcamp — the largest industry focused accelerator network in the world with 16 programs across five continents. ', 'We created Rainmaking Loft coworking spaces. Serving over 1,000 entrepreneurs in London, Berlin and Copenhagen.', 'We have built 25 of our own startups, achieving 5 notable exits and lead over 350 startup investments. ', 'We partner with organizations to deliver training. Engage with startups. Build digital products and launch new ventures.', 'We give you the mindset, skills and confidence to ideate, create and scale new business.   Collaboratively and confidently. No buzzwords. Just plain English.  \r\nAnd we’ll make sure it happens. We love results not presentations. Actions not words. \r\n\r\nJust see for yourself.', 'We live in a world that is changing faster than ever. Where past performance is no guarantee of future success. We know from experience that no matter how well you plan new ventures, sometimes they just don’t work. This is part of our approach to helping our partners discover innovation for their own organizations. If something works – or if it doesn’t – you’ll know about it.   Many claim to have the answers but hide behind powerpoint presentations and buzzwords. We accept that we don\'t have all the answers, but we do know the right questions to ask.   Read the latest thoughts and lessons learned from experts across the Rainmaking community. ', 'We love results, not presentations. ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Founder Name', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-17 13:25:02', '2016-11-16 10:30:15', '43471c69-52ea-418f-980d-13b384d5b548'),
 ('3', '3', 'en_us', 'hi Craft!', '<p>Craft is the CMS that’s powering Localhost. It’s beautiful, powerful, flexible, and easy-to-use, and it’s made by Pixel &amp; Tonic. We can’t wait to dive in and see what it’s capable of!</p>\n\n<!--pagebreak-->\n\n<p>This is even more captivating content, which you couldn’t see on the News index page because it was entered after a Page Break, and the News index template only likes to show the content on the first page.</p>\n\n<p>Craft: a nice alternative to Word, if you’re making a website.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-17 13:25:03', '2016-10-17 14:06:48', '5ad8f461-376d-406e-81a7-1a4934bb2d22'),
 ('6', '6', 'en_us', 'Our Story', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Our journey — a cheesy leading header', 'We partner with global corporations across multiple sectors to validate business ideas, foster valuable commercial partnerships and dramatically accelerate growth for our portfolio startups.\r\n\r\nYour time is better spent actively learning and applying new ways of working than admiring our type choices and image selections. Sure, we\'ve been known to whip up a diagram or two, but you\'ll never receive the traditional consulting treatment from us: long on slides, short on action. ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-17 17:22:40', '2016-11-17 10:27:02', '0ee0015a-8f7c-4803-8370-edb985b0bda8'),
 ('7', '7', 'en_us', 'Who We Are', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'Everyone at Rainmaking lives and breathes the entrepreneurial spirit. We started in 2006 as a collective of serial entrepreneurs, sharing in the both the risks and the rewards of starting new businesses. Since then, we have grown into a global community of entrepreneurs, investors and ex-corporate executives. Driven to create something new, to make a difference.  ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-17 17:23:07', '2016-11-15 16:59:29', '7b929f77-8650-470e-8907-bfd782e1421f'),
 ('8', '8', 'en_us', '25 of our own startups', '<p>Creating companies and bringing them to market is our first love. Together, we’ve built over 25 of our own startups, achieved 5 notable exits and participated in more than 350 investments. Here are just a few active companies that we have built. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '25 startups, 5 exits, 350+ investments', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-17 17:24:05', '2016-11-14 17:06:39', 'b7c6029e-4b5a-432b-8afa-e4107a09d4a3'),
 ('9', '9', 'en_us', '16 programs in 13 cities', '<p>Since we founded Startupbootcamp in 2010, it’s become one of the world’s leading, industry specific accelerator programs, driving collaboration between startups and corporate partners across entire ecosystems. To date we have 16 programs in 13 cities across the globe with a presence in every major geography. </p>\n\n<p>Startups come to us looking for the right partners, investors and mentors to take the next step forward. Our corporate partners come to us to find the next big thing and gain access to a global network.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Startupbootcamp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-17 17:24:18', '2016-11-17 10:20:49', 'fa9dda69-6d83-4a20-a184-5180a89f4fb6'),
 ('10', '10', 'en_us', 'Building spaces to connect and learn', '<p>Over the last ten years, we have created a global community of startups, bringing entrepreneurs, investors and corporate partners together. Our co-working spaces in Berlin, Copenhagen and London are now home to over 1,000 entrepreneurs – and there’s always room for new arrivals. Expect hackathons, lively debates, new ideas and networking events with industry and government figures. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Rainmaking Loft', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-17 17:24:30', '2016-11-14 17:08:11', 'a555957e-f3be-49ae-9afc-22ac6c8c82ea'),
 ('11', '11', 'en_us', 'Rainmaking Voices', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-17 17:35:53', '2016-11-15 16:58:03', 'e67d77fd-ee83-45d0-8cbe-4bdf4ac09baf'),
 ('12', '12', 'en_us', 'Events ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'We explore ideas in entrepreneurship and business through the many events that we host throughout the year. Join the discussion and find an event near you. ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-17 17:36:05', '2016-11-15 16:58:14', '74d902b3-4deb-498f-bc77-1a65c36a4bc8'),
