 ('186', '277', 'en_us', 'Jordan Schlipf', '<p>Jordan is an entrepreneur, investor, and educator. He has been both a VC and angel investor and has launched companies in multiple verticals and markets. Jordan is an expert in Lean Startup and design thinking, and has created educational programs for accelerators, universities, corporates and governments. He now leads our venture studio, building multiple new startups in parallel, alongside our fortune 500 partners.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://uk.linkedin.com/in/jordan-schlipf-0b855174', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'https://twitter.com/jordups', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-27 17:52:06', '2016-11-08 16:21:25', '3467c29a-ecae-43a2-b9e6-e1d4c6ea53fe'),
