 ('190', '281', 'en_us', 'Carsten Kølbek', '<p>Carsten has successfully founded seven businesses including Rainmaking Loft and Startupbootcamp. He draws on over ten years of executive and board level experience in engineering, technical consulting and innovation management at major companies such as Accenture and VIA Travel. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://uk.linkedin.com/in/ckoelbek', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'https://twitter.com/carstenkolbek', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-28 13:25:33', '2016-10-28 13:47:40', '2ffab082-9fee-4080-a64e-f1e75f17afc1'),
 ('191', '282', 'en_us', 'Jakob Kistorp', '<p>Jakob has globally sourced thousands of startups for clients, helped build and run accelerators, and delivered projects in over 15 countries. He specializes in helping cities and countries to establish and grow self-sustaining startup ecosystems. He co-founded Startup MENA, leading to increased startup funding and the creation of hundreds of new jobs across 9 countries in the region.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://dk.linkedin.com/in/jakobkistorp', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'https://twitter.com/Kistorp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-28 13:26:53', '2016-11-01 09:43:43', 'a0e5d28c-bc74-4b65-a7c6-da7c04b633ba'),
 ('192', '283', 'en_us', 'Martin Bjergegaard', '<p>Martin spent time as a strategy consultant at McKinsey before finding entrepreneurship as a tool for global change. In the last 20 years Martin has built 10 companies and published three books which have been sold in 35 countries. He recently won the prestigious British Library, Management Book of the Year for his book <em>How to Be a Leader.</em></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://dk.linkedin.com/in/martinbjergegaard', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'https://twitter.com/bjergegaard', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-28 13:27:35', '2016-10-28 13:46:02', '868ef2ee-09fa-4b47-8f08-433d6d3f3cfe'),
