 ('15', '9', '10', '1', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Accelerator\",\"slug\":\"accelerator\",\"postDate\":1476725058,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>Since we co-founded Startupbootcamp in 2006, it\\u2019s become one of the world\\u2019s leading, industry specific accelerator programs, driving collaboration between startups and established players across entire ecosystems. To date we have 16 programs in 13 cities across the globe with a presence in every major geography. Startups come to us looking for the right partners, investors and mentors to take the next step forward. Our corporate partners come to us to find the next big thing and gain access to a global network.<\\/p>\",\"62\":\"The world\'s leading accelerator program\"}}', '2016-10-21 13:23:10', '2016-10-21 13:23:10', 'f85d04a1-c81b-4a0c-a939-57f6efdd9865'),
