nges for FinTech all have the opportunity to contribute, so, we involved over 250 people across all levels of the ecosystem, from executives to developers.\\u00a0\",\"backgroundColour\":\"white\"}},\"227\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Download the Summary Report Here\",\"text\":\"Recommendations for Making Copenhagen a Nordic FinTech Hub \",\"image\":[\"228\"],\"align\":\"right\"}},\"174\":{\"type\":\"videoBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"youtubeVideoId\":\"QD7STd0ZP88\"}}},\"80\":\"\",\"72\":[\"175\"],\"67\":\"It was an absolute privilege to take part in a study that could have such a huge impact for a relatively small city and also a massive global industry\",\"69\":\"Partner at Rainmaking\",\"68\":\"Carsten K\\u00f8lbek\",\"71\":[\"229\"]}}', '2016-10-26 15:51:00', '2016-10-26 15:51:00', '5c60d186-0134-45d0-bf4e-f5b423c0d3b1'),
 ('91', '195', '4', '15', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"15\",\"title\":\"How Lloyd\'s Banking Group Stays Ahead of FinTech Evolution\",\"slug\":\"how-lloyds-banking-group-stays-ahead-of-fintech-evolution\",\"postDate\":1477478580,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"70\":[\"178\"],\"47\":{\"196\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Partnering With Market Leaders\",\"text\":\"Since 2014 we have been helping to shape the global evolution of FinTech. Together with market leaders like MasterCard, Lloyds Banking Group, Santander, Thomson Reuters, PWC and Rabobank we are running Startupbootcamp accelerator programs for startups and designing corporate innovation programs, establishing commercial connections between startups and established players.\",\"image\":[\"180\"],\"align\":\"left\"}},\"197\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Global Change With Top Startups\",\"text\":\"Each year we scout upwards of 3000 FinTech startups from across the globe. With accelerator programs in Singapore, London and New York, and 50+ FinTech events across almost every continent. \",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"198\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"\\\"Each year we scout upwards of 3,000 FinTech startups from across the globe\\\"\",\"image\":[\"179\"]}},\"199\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Early Access to Innovation\",\"text\":\"We select less than 1% of these startups for a Startupbootcamp cohort. This ensures our partners are collaborating with the best talent, often generating pilots, commercial partnerships and co-created solutions. Meanwhile, through the selection process itself, partners are exposed to evolving technology and business model trends at an early stage.  \",\"image\":[\"181\"],\"align\":\"right\"}},\"200\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Staying in Front of the Curve with Lloyd\'s \",\"text\":\"Lloyds Banking Group has been a partner on our Startupbootcamp FinTech program since 2014. The partnership came at a time when the bank was undertaking a large-scale digital transformation program, and presented an ideal platform to test new ideas and connect with the wider FinTech ecosystem. \",\"backgroundColour\":\"black\"}},\"201\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"\",\"text\":\"Lloyds\\u2019 goal is to scan the market for innovation and find new opportunities to provide better service to their customers. The relationship is beneficial for both parties: the FinTech startup has access to subject matter experts, launching customers and scarce assets like data sets. For Lloyds it is beneficial because they are able to learn about new technology, business models, see the results within the market and deduce important lessons to stay ahead and deliver value to their customers. \",\"image\":[\"182\"],\"align\":\"left\"}},\"202\":{\"type\":\"quoteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"The relationship with Startupbootcamp has been the first step towards collaborating with startups and to support our digital transformation agenda. By working with innovative partners we are able to deliver even better customer propositions and services.\",\"quoteName\":\"Claire Calmejane\",\"role\":\"Head of Innovation\",\"image\":[\"189\"]}},\"203\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"Keen to partner with Statupbootcamp\\u2019s portofolio companies, Lloyds has worked with alumni WoraPay \\u2013 a collaboration which is said to have saved Lloyds Banking Group employees 10,000 days of work. \",\"image\":[\"185\"]}},\"204\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"New Ways of Working\",\"text\":\"For Lloyds, collaborating with the FinTech sector also provides inspiring examples of agility and working practices that refresh Lloyd\\u2019s thinking and approach to delivering digital services. \\r\\n\\r\\nThe partnership gave Lloyds the chance to be involved in dedicated events such as FinTech Lounges and hackathons, presenting another opportunity to experience new ways of working.\\r\\n\",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"205\":{\"type\":\"imageBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"191\",\"193\",\"194\"]}}},\"80\":\"\",\"72\":[\"179\"],\"67\":\"Our relationship with Rainmaking has given hundreds of our employees access to new tools and skillsets that they have used to become inspiring intrepreneurs inside Lloyds Banking Group.\\r\\n\",\"69\":\"Head of Innovation\",\"68\":\"Claire Calmejane\",\"71\":[\"189\"]}}', '2016-10-26 15:52:32', '2016-10-26 15:52:32', 'ed1b7967-d458-494a-b589-1e54de8e07f0'),
 ('92', '195', '4', '15', 'en_us', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"15\",\"title\":\"How Lloyd\'s Banking Group Stays Ahead of FinTech Evolution\",\"slug\":\"how-lloyds-banking-group-stays-ahead-of-fintech-evolution\",\"postDate\":1477478580,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"70\":[\"178\"],\"47\":{\"196\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Partnering With Market Leaders\",\"text\":\"Since 2014 we have been helping to shape the global evolution of FinTech. Together with market leaders like MasterCard, Lloyds Banking Group, Santander, Thomson Reuters, PWC and Rabobank we are running Startupbootcamp accelerator programs for startups and designing corporate innovation programs, establishing commercial connections between startups and established players.\",\"image\":[\"180\"],\"align\":\"left\"}},\"198\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"Each year we scout upwards of 3000 FinTech startups from across the globe. With accelerator programs in Singapore, London and New York, and 50+ FinTech events across almost every continent. \",\"image\":[\"179\"]}},\"199\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Early Access to Innovation\",\"text\":\"We select less than 1% of these startups for a Startupbootcamp cohort. This ensures our partners are collaborating with the best talent, often generating pilots, commercial partnerships and co-created solutions. Meanwhile, through the selection process itself, partners are exposed to evolving technology and business model trends at an early stage.  \",\"image\":[\"181\"],\"align\":\"right\"}},\"200\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Staying in Front of the Curve with Lloyd\'s \",\"text\":\"Lloyds Banking Group has been a partner on our Startupbootcamp FinTech program since 2014. The partnership came at a time when the bank was undertaking a large-scale