impressive community of alumni, mentors and investors.\\u201d\",\"69\":\"Senior Manager, Business Innovation\",\"68\":\"Dr. Frank Spennemann\",\"71\":[\"55\"]}}', '2016-10-27 13:54:59', '2016-10-27 13:54:59', 'c16f0652-d553-48d4-a34a-2ecf94a98a17'),
 ('143', '86', '4', '15', 'en_us', '7', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"15\",\"title\":\"Bolstering Trade and Cooperation Between the EU and GCC\",\"slug\":\"bolstering-trade-investment-and-cooperation-between-the-eu-and-gcc\",\"postDate\":1477400400,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"70\":[\"218\"],\"47\":{\"87\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Collaboration Between SME\'s, Startups, and Corporates\",\"text\":\"Following the success of our ecosystem development work in the MENA regions, we were trusted to co-create the 2015 EU-GCC program. A pilot initiative intended to promote trade between the EU and GCC as well as increase cooperation between corporates, SME\\u2019s and startups.\\r\\n\\r\\nWe partnered with The Danish Confederation of Industry, Business Europe, and the Federation of Gulf Cooperation Council Chambers (\\u2018GCC\\u2019) to design and deliver this project, funded by the EU Commission.\",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"88\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Optimizing Relations\",\"text\":\"Despite a past characterized by sociopolitical challenges, the GCC and EU are increasingly reliant on each other for trade and investment. The GCC stands as the fifth top trading partner with the EU and accounts for over \\u20ac100 Billion in EU goods exports. \\r\\n\\r\\nWhile trade is increasing steadily year over year, the majority is still based on mineral fuels and industrial products. \",\"image\":[\"84\"],\"align\":\"left\"}},\"89\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"Our challenge was to promote trade bilaterally in underrepresented areas such as services and technology, while also increasing collaboration in the development of new innovations.\",\"image\":[\"85\"]}},\"95\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Building on Existing Platforms\",\"text\":\"Having already built up a strong local presence in the GCC region and Europe, and proven the success of our workshop format through our Startup MENA Program, we were able to draw on our existing network of engaged corporates and ecosystem players to design a series of premium workshops and match-making events.\",\"backgroundColour\":\"white\"}},\"96\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"\",\"text\":\"Over the course of 2015 we ran 24 events across 10 countries, successfully highlighting disruptive startups from the GCC, training entrepreneurs, matching corporates to startups for commercial partnerships, and promoting the Gulf as a market to EU startups and SMEs.\",\"image\":[\"91\"],\"align\":\"right\"}},\"97\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"We Designed and Delivered:\",\"text\":\"Intensive workshops in Kuwait City, Doha, Muscat, Dubai, Manama, Jeddah, London, Berlin, Brussels and Rome\\r\\n\\r\\nMatch-making events in London and Dubai\\r\\n\\r\\nAn international pitch challenge which toured Kuwait, Bahrain, UAE, Qatar, Saudi Arabia and Oman\\r\\n\\r\\nAn online opportunity matchmaking portal: EU-GCC Connect\\r\\n\",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"98\":{\"type\":\"imageBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"92\",\"93\"]}},\"99\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Continuous Improvement\",\"text\":\"Building on the success of the EU-GCC program in 2015, the initiative will continue to run until 2018.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe data and reports generated by Rainmaking will be used as the bedrock of further efforts to increase trade and investment across various industries.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe Danish Confederation of Industry, Business Europe, and the Federation of Gulf Cooperation Council Chambers are all driven to to progress further; forging closer links, removing regulatory barriers, and increasing trade.\",\"backgroundColour\":\"black\"}}},\"80\":\"\",\"72\":[\"94\"],\"67\":\"It was an absolutely amazing experience to help talented entrepreneurs while simultaneously increasing international cooperation.\",\"69\":\"Rainmaking Partner\",\"68\":\"Jakob Kistorp\",\"71\":[\"214\"]}}', '2016-10-27 14:05:01', '2016-10-27 14:05:01', '1399b66e-1564-4a1a-b039-c7a3a1e4f4cf'),
 ('144', '6', '6', '1', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Our Story\",\"slug\":\"our-story\",\"postDate\":1476724960,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"47\":\"\",\"63\":\"We partner with global corporations across multiple sectors to validate business ideas, foster valuable commercial partnerships and dramatically accelerate growth for our portfolio startups.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour time is better spent actively learning and applying new ways of working than admiring our type choices and image selections. Sure, we\'ve been known to whip up a diagram or two, but you\'ll never receive the traditional consulting treatment from us: long on slides, short on action. \",\"62\":\"Our journey \\u2014 a cheesy leading header\"}}', '2016-10-27 14:12:04', '2016-10-27 14:12:04', '314492ce-bbba-41e5-b3ef-bc61c4b644ee'),
