\"67\":\"It was an absolutely amazing experience to help talented entrepreneurs while simultaneously increasing international cooperation.\",\"69\":\"Rainmaking Partner\",\"68\":\"Jakob Kistorp\",\"71\":[\"214\"]}}', '2016-10-27 14:14:00', '2016-10-27 14:14:00', '0805bf76-1694-4e68-82d2-392570bc4d0c'),
