 a strong local presence in the GCC region and Europe, and proven the success of our workshop format through our Startup MENA Program, we were able to draw on our existing network of engaged corporates and ecosystem players to design a series of premium workshops and match-making events.\",\"backgroundColour\":\"white\"}},\"96\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"24 Events in 10 Countries \",\"text\":\"Over the course of 2015 we ran 24 events across 10 countries. And, successfully highlighted disruptive startups from the GCC, training entrepreneurs, matching corporates to startups for commercial partnerships, and promoting the Gulf as a market to EU startups and SMEs.\",\"image\":[\"91\"],\"align\":\"right\"}},\"97\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"We Designed and Delivered:\",\"text\":\"Intensive workshops in Kuwait City, Doha, Muscat, Dubai, Manama, Jeddah, London, Berlin, Brussels and Rome\\r\\n\\r\\nMatch-making events in London and Dubai\\r\\n\\r\\nAn international pitch challenge touring Kuwait, Bahrain, UAE, Qatar, Saudi Arabia and Oman\\r\\n\\r\\nAn online matchmaking portal: EU-GCC Connect\\r\\n\",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"98\":{\"type\":\"imageBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"92\",\"93\"]}},\"99\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Continued Operation\",\"text\":\"Building on the success of the EU-GCC program in 2015, the initiative will continue to run until 2018.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe data and reports generated by Rainmaking will be used as the bedrock of further efforts to increase trade and investment across various industries.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe Danish Confederation of Industry, Business Europe, and the Federation of Gulf Cooperation Council Chambers are all driven to to progress further; forging closer links, removing regulatory barriers, and increasing trade.\",\"backgroundColour\":\"black\"}}},\"80\":\"\",\"72\":[\"94\"],\"67\":\"It was an absolutely amazing experience to help talented entrepreneurs while simultaneously increasing international cooperation.\",\"69\":\"Rainmaking Partner\",\"68\":\"Jakob Kistorp\",\"71\":[\"214\"]}}', '2016-10-27 14:19:02', '2016-10-27 14:19:02', '526eaeaa-e9e4-441f-935c-1c6e97a79770'),
 ('147', '253', '15', '1', 'en_us', '1', NULL, '{\"typeId\":\"15\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Partnership Index\",\"slug\":\"partnership-index\",\"postDate\":1477578627,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":[]}', '2016-10-27 14:30:29', '2016-10-27 14:30:29', '074672b5-d959-48ec-b037-642d5a101d2d'),
 ('148', '69', '4', '15', 'en_us', '9', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"15\",\"title\":\"Sourcing Startups to Catapult Castrol\\u2019s Business Forward\",\"slug\":\"strategically-sourcing-startups-to-catapult-castrols-business-forward\",\"postDate\":1477395000,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"70\":[\"64\"],\"47\":{\"74\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Going Beyond Motor Oil\",\"text\":\"In 2012, we were approached by Castrol innoVentures to help increase its deal flow and strengthen its presence and visibility in the global startup community.\\u00a0\\r\\n\\r\\nAt the time, Castrol had just set up its strategic innovation and investment arm in order to bring additional value to its existing business areas, and to take Castrol beyond motor oils and lubricants and into future focused revenue streams.\\r\\n\\r\\nTogether with the team at Castrol innoVentures, we designed a global pitch competition to act as a sourcing and screening program, allowing us to meet and evaluate startups relevant for Castrol to work with. \\r\\n\\r\\nThe program resulted in Castrol making a direct investment in one startup and commercial partnerships with seven others. \",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"71\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"\\\"we were approached by Castrol innoVentures to help increase its deal flow and strengthen its presence and visibility in the global startup community.\\\"\",\"image\":[\"68\"]}},\"72\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"How to Put Castrol On the Global Startup Map\",\"text\":\"In today\\u2019s venture capital environment, startups are not short on sources of investment. There are hundreds of institutional firms, angel investors and CVC\\u2019s. \\r\\n\\r\\nWe needed a way to put Castrol on startups\\u2019 radar as a valuable partner, both to work with, and to have on their cap table. \\r\\n\\r\\nThe focus was for us to find startups innovating in 4 strategic areas: Smart Mobility, next generation engineering, intelligent operations, and responsible Castrol.\",\"backgroundColour\":\"black\"}},\"75\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Building a Startup Friendly Brand\",\"text\":\"We built a brand around the project: the Castrol 20\\/20 Challenge. \\r\\n\\r\\nA selection of startup finalists would receive free flights and accommodation to London or Shanghai in order to pitch their business to Venture Capitalists and Castrol executives. The winning team was to receive 10,000 USD.\\r\\n\\r\\nA brand website was launched, promoting the competition to potential applicants and spreading the word throughout the global startup community. Both the brand and website were fundamental in positioning Castrol as a company ready to make investments and meaningfully engage with startups.\",\"image\":[\"73\"],\"align\":\"right\"}},\"76\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Over 2,000 Startups Reviewed\",\"text\":\"With our marketing efforts driving competition applications, and outreach from our dedicated sourcing team, we attracted and reviewed over 2,000 startups.\\r\\n\\r\\nDrawing on our experience mentoring and selecting startups for our Startupbootcamp programs and our own investments, we created a shortlist of 20 companies based on their applications and 1-1 interviews.\\r\\n\\r\\nTogether with Castrol innoVentures, we conducted further interviews to narrow the selection to just five startups in each of two competition finals in London and Shanghai.\",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"77\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Preparing Startups for Collaboration with Corporates\",\"text\":\"In both London and Shanghai, we worked with the startups and mentors one day prior to the final events to prepare the teams. We helped them hone their pitches and introduced ways that they could more effectively work with major corporations.  \\r\\n\\r\\nThe following day, the startups pitched and met with over 30 Venture Capitalists, alongside executives from Castrol and other notable corporations like 3M.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe events not only provided immense value to the startups, in terms of connections and networking with experts, but also gave Castrol a platform to engage with the startups early on.\",\"image\":[\"67\"],\"align\":\"left\"}},\"82\":{\"type\":\"imageBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"79\",\"80\",\"81\"]}},\"78\":{\"type\":\"quoteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"\\\"Castrol 2020 Challenge provided impressive and innovative ideas and we work with 7 out of 10 teams from the 2012 program\\\"\",\"quoteName\":\"Roy Williamson\",\"role\":\"Castrol InnoVentures, Managing Director\",\"image\":[\"66\"]}},\"83\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Creating and Capitalising on Investment Opportunities\",\"text\":\"Castrol InnoVentures ultimately invested in Greensteam, a ground breaking technology company specialising in energy saving solutions for commercial vessels.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe events proved to be a success, so we hosted a second edition, this time exclusively in Shanghai.\\r\\n\\r\\nTo this day, Castrol innoVentures remains an active player in the mobility space and has made further investments in a range of startups.\\r\\n\",\"image\":[\"65\"],\"align\":\"left\"}}},\"80\":\"1\",\"72\":[\"65\"],\"67\":\"\\\"The Castrol 20\\/20 Challenge provided impressive and innovative ideas leading to us working with 7 out of 10 startups from the program\\\"\",\"69\":\"Managing Director, Castrol InnoVentures\",\"68\":\"Roy Williamson\",\"71\":[\"66\"]}}', '2016-10-27 14:39:04', '2016-10-27 14:39:04', '1c742c3b-8114-45a5-bab1-d11a24ed3aa3'),
 ('149', '253', '15', '1', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Partnership Index\",\"slug\":\"partnership-index\",\"postDate\":1477578627,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"63\":\"We don\\u2019t just think about products and prepare slide presentations. We build products and services and scale companies around them. Practising what we preach. Actions not words. Just see for yourself.\"}}', '2016-10-27 14:52:36', '2016-10-27 14:52:36', '96b5fe92-eec2-4d5b-883b-1c4b3b0cd61a'),
 ('150', '108', '4', '15', 'en_us', '4', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"15\",\"title\":\"From Idea to Business: Employee Powered Innovation at Majid Al Futtaim\",\"slug\":\"from-idea-to-business-employee-powered-innovation-at-majid-al-futtaim\",\"postDate\":1477406580,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"70\":[\"106\"],\"47\":{\"109\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"A three day hackathon followed by an intensive five day program, transforming ideas into viable businesses.\",\"image\":[\"100\"]}},\"110\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Responding To Changing Times\",\"text\":\"Majid Al Futtaim runs Malls and Carrefour hypermarkets across the Middle East, North Africa and Central Asia including the Mall of the Emirates, famous for its indoor ski slope. \\r\\n \\r\\nTheir large physical footprint has given them a distinctive advantage in the retail market, however, with consumer behaviors evolving towards an increasingly digital experience, Majid Al Futtaim wanted to explore how they could be more innovative; both in their customer experiences, and their ways of working.\",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"111\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"48 Hours to Create a New Experience for Dubai\",\"text\":\"As the first phase of the \\u201cNext Great Moment\\u201d challenge, we created a two day hackathon. This inspired Majid Al Futtaim\\u2019s employees to refine internal ideas for new and innovative products and services in just 48 hours. \\r\\n\\r\\nIn addition to generating new and innovative ideas, the event gave employees direct experience applying a more entrepreneurial mindset. It also served to create both internal and external excitement around Majid Al Futtaim\'s innovative approach. \",\"image\":[\"101\"],\"align\":\"left\"}},\"112\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"\",\"text\":\"From over 1300 applications, 83 talented individuals were selected to attend this intensive experience. By bringing together employees from across the company, we reinforced the importance of collaboration to drive innovation and escape the natural silos of the organization. \",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"113\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Thinking Big\",\"text\":\"Each attendee had just 60 seconds to pitch their idea, before teams formed around the 10 most popular concepts.\\r\\n\\r\\nThey then had just two days to test and evolve their value proposition through customer interviews, and industry research. Finally, they distilled their updated business idea into a 3 minute pitch.\\r\\n\\r\\nThroughout the weekend, teams were exposed to new methodologies; an intensive series of exercises and workshops which encouraged attendees to \\u201cThink Big\\u201d, introducing them to Global Trends to further inspire their efforts.\\r\\n\",\"image\":[\"102\"],\"align\":\"right\"}},\"114\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"\\\"From over 1300 applications, 83 talented individuals were selected to attend this intensive experience.\\\"\",\"image\":[\"100\"]}},\"115\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Making the Most of Every Minute\",\"text\":\"We held networking events and icebreakers to encourage teams to utilize the event to meet as many colleagues and industry experts as possible.\\r\\n\\r\\nExpert pitch trainers taught the teams to present with impact, polishing their pitches, and honing presentation skills.\\r\\n\\r\\nMeanwhile, serial entrepreneurs and thought leaders were on hand to offer the teams mentoring and further training, inspiring participants with startup approaches to propel them forward.\",\"image\":[\"103\"],\"align\":\"right\"}},\"116\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Ideas to Move You: From Dubai to London\",\"text\":\"In this supportive, yet challenging, environment, ideas evolved rapidly. \\r\\nA wide range of concepts were developed throughout this process; offering MAF a choice of radically innovative solutions, alongside those which could be quickly implemented.\\r\\n\\r\\nTwo of the most exciting ideas won the prize of 5 weeks in London with Rainmaking. Here, we created an immersive Pop-Up Lab which pushed their business models, teamwork and delivery even further.\",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"117\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"\\\"Two of the most exciting ideas won the prize of 5 weeks in London with Rainmaking.\\\"\",\"image\":[\"104\"]}},\"176\":{\"type\":\"videoBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"youtubeVideoId\":\"yEzjhZOcJAg\"}},\"118\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"New Skills and New Business\",\"text\":\"These teams left the Pop-Up Lab with a new appreciation of Lean Startup approaches, experience conducting customer interviews, and greater insight into working collaboratively in a newly formed team. Equipped with new ways of approaching problems and understanding customer needs they are more able to create meaningful change to MAF\'s business. \",\"image\":[\"105\"],\"align\":\"left\"}}},\"80\":\"\",\"72\":[\"100\"],\"67\":\"The Innovation Challenge provides a unique opportunity for us to foster a culture of innovation amongst our people.\",\"69\":\"CEO, MAF Ventures\",\"68\":\"Galal Ismail\",\"71\":[\"107\"]}}', '2016-10-27 14:54:17', '2016-10-27 14:54:17', 'c46921cd-97ea-4aa8-ab8b-1b30ba0bc21b'),
 ('151', '129', '4', '15', 'en_us', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"15\",\"title\":\"Sourcing Europe\'s Best EdTech Startups for Collaboration With Sanoma\",\"slug\":\"sourcing-europes-best-edtech-startups-for-collaboration-with-sanoma\",\"postDate\":1477412460,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"70\":[\"127\"],\"47\":{\"130\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Strategic Deal Flow: A Win-Win\",\"text\":\"For this project we were entrusted with finding hopeful EdTech startups with the potential to grow their business together with Sanoma, the Nordic region\\u2019s leading media and learning company.\\r\\n\\r\\nPromising startups were invited to participate in the \\u201cSanoma Startup Challenge - the future of learning,\\u201d an event which we designed and delivered to discover promising startup talent.\",\"image\":[\"122\"],\"align\":\"left\"}},\"131\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"The Future of Learning\",\"text\":\"Sanoma Ventures came to us looking for ways to find high quality deal flow for their newly formed corporate venture fund. \\r\\n\\r\\nThe media and education space has been making a steady shift away from traditional print and television to new models of delivery and distribution. Seeing the trend, Sanoma sought to partner and invest in startups that could provide different ways to reach students, distribute information and produce content.\",\"backgroundColour\":\"black\"}},\"132\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"5 Converge to Compete in Amsterdam\",\"text\":\"Using our existing networks through our Startupbootcamp programs and dedicated research team we began surveying Europe for startups that could supply innovative shifts in Sanoma\\u2019s  business model.\\r\\n\\r\\nOur efforts spanned 22 European countries. We evaluated over 500 startups, encouraging over 100 high quality applications. From these, we hand-picked the best 50 to participate in the challenge.\\r\\nThe top 5 teams won an all-expenses paid trip to Amsterdam for the competition Final.\",\"image\":[\"123\"],\"align\":\"right\"}},\"133\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"\\\"Our efforts spanned 22 European countries. We evaluated over 500 startups, encouraging over 100 high quality applications. From these, we hand-picked the best 50 to participate in the challenge.\\\"\",\"image\":[\"123\"]}},\"134\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"\",\"text\":\"The two-day competition offered startups the chance to work with mentors, Sanoma executives, Sanoma Learning industry experts and SanomaVenture\\u2019s investment team. \\r\\n\\r\\nBy exposing startups to these potential partners and customers, we pushed them to evolve their ideas, while demonstrating the potential benefits of collaboration between corporations and startups.\",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"135\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Value for Both Sides of the Table\",\"text\":\"As a part of the Sanoma Startup Challenge, the startups were given the opportunity to make their final pitch at THENEXTWEB conference in Amsterdam, live on stage in front of Sanoma executives, investors and the full conference crowd.\\r\\n\\r\\nUltimately, a Danish startup, Labster, which offers next generation laboratory simulations, was named the winner, receiving a cash prize of \\u20ac25,000.\\r\\n\\r\\nTo date, Sanoma has invested in 18 different ed-tech startups.\",\"image\":[\"124\"],\"align\":\"right\"}}},\"80\":\"\",\"72\":[\"124\"],\"67\":\"We were pleasantly surprised by the diversity and the high quality of the startups that applied ... the challenge has already given us interesting new connections for both SanomaVentures, for potential investments, as for Sanoma Learning for future cooperation and partnerships\",\"69\":\"Herman Kienhuis\",\"68\":\"Investment Director\",\"71\":[\"225\"]}}', '2016-10-27 14:59:53', '2016-10-27 14:59:53', '5bc48ad0-f214-4a0d-a981-0fdde9cea8f0'),
 ('152', '12', '13', '1', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Events Page Copy\",\"slug\":\"events-page-copy\",\"postDate\":1476725765,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"63\":\"Your time is better spent actively learning and applying new ways of working than admiring our type choices and image selections. Sure, we\'ve been known to whip up a diagram or two, but you\'ll never receive the traditional consulting treatment from us: long on slides, short on action. \",\"62\":\"\"}}', '2016-10-27 15:09:08', '2016-10-27 15:09:08', '2d58dd8b-52a9-44f9-930e-e3ed047b4762'),
 ('153', '253', '15', '1', 'en_us', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Partnership Index\",\"slug\":\"partnership-index\",\"postDate\":1477578627,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"63\":\"Text: Innovation defies definition. It\\u2019s as unique, complex and thrilling as every business we\\u2019ve ever worked with. If years of experience have taught us one thing, it\\u2019s this: the best definition of innovation is to find your own.  \\r\\n\\r\\nWe can help you do that. Collaboratively and confidently. No bluster, no buzzwords. Just plain English.  And we\\u2019ll make sure it happens. We love results, not presentations. Actions not words.  Just see for yourself.\"}}', '2016-10-27 15:10:00', '2016-10-27 15:10:00', '6257b50a-d273-48fd-af0c-3a3ca863706c'),
 ('154', '11', '12', '1', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Blog index copy\",\"slug\":\"blog-index-copy\",\"postDate\":1476725753,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"63\":\"We explore ideas in entrepreneurship and business through the many events that we host throughout the year. Join the discussion and find an event near you. \",\"62\":\"\"}}', '2016-10-27 15:10:30', '2016-10-27 15:10:30', '44f21465-46db-4003-b3d9-8a66fbf22c78'),
 ('155', '12', '13', '1', 'en_us', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Events Page Copy\",\"slug\":\"events-page-copy\",\"postDate\":1476725765,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"63\":\"We explore ideas in entrepreneurship and business through the many events that we host throughout the year. Join the discussion and find an event near you. \",\"62\":\"\"}}', '2016-10-27 15:10:33', '2016-10-27 15:10:33', '03a1f123-9211-485b-b90e-a6c6612897a3'),
 ('156', '158', '4', '15', 'en_us', '6', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"15\",\"title\":\"Startup MENA: Empowering Entrepreneurship in the Middle East and North Africa\",\"slug\":\"startup-mena-empowering-entrepreneurs-in-the-middle-east-and-north-africa\",\"postDate\":1477415700,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"70\":[\"156\"],\"47\":{\"159\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"In 2014, we partnered with The Danish Foreign Ministry to deliver a 2 year program stimulating economic growth in the private sectors of Egypt, Jordan and Tunisia. \",\"image\":[\"147\"]}},\"160\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Seeding a Startup Ecosystem\",\"text\":\"Since 2003 The Danish government has been actively collaborating with the Middle East and North Africa to strengthen cooperation and support the ongoing reform and democratization of the region.\\r\\n\\r\\nHowever, political revolution and unemployment still threaten to impede the successful democratization process in some countries in the region. Stimulating job creation has therefore become a key objective for The Danish-Arab Partnership Program across the region. \",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"161\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Job Creation in the MENA Region\",\"text\":\"In 2014, high rates of unemployment continued, particularly amongst young people, despite many being well-educated, ready to work and keen to actively help shape the future of their countries. \\r\\n\\r\\nIt was in this context that we were challenged to design and deliver a program with The Danish Foreign Ministry: creating jobs and growth through entrepreneurship.\",\"image\":[\"151\"],\"align\":\"left\"}},\"162\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Leading Through Value \",\"text\":\"As our team was new to the region, we knew that the existing ecosystem would measure us on the basis of the value we displayed. To ensure our event attendees left with new insights, knowledge, and inspiration, we brought in experts, high-profile international mentors, and investors to all our events.\",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"163\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"We Delivered a Range of Events to Support and Encourage Local Startups:\",\"text\":\"\\u2022 Two investment labs\\r\\n\\u2022 Two 48 hour hackathons\\r\\n\\u2022 Four women\\u2019s meetups\\r\\n\\u2022 Six mini bootcamps\\r\\n\\u2022 Three open offices\\r\\n\\u2022 Two job fairs\\r\\n\\u2022 Two investor pitch events\\r\\n\\u2022 One corporate matchmaking event\\r\\n\\u2022 A series of intensive, high impact workshops\\r\\n\",\"image\":[\"150\"],\"align\":\"right\"}},\"164\":{\"type\":\"imageBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"152\",\"153\",\"154\",\"155\"]}},\"165\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Over Two Years We Hosted 27 Events Across Jordan, Egypt and Tunisia \",\"text\":\"+ 90 jobs created\\r\\n+ 820 entrepreneurs\\r\\n+ 70 partners\\r\\n+ 130 startups engaged\\r\\n+ 160 mentors engaged\\r\\n+ 10.000 in network\\r\\n\",\"backgroundColour\":\"white\"}},\"226\":{\"type\":\"videoBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"youtubeVideoId\":\"9B-fW-MSg5Q\"}}},\"80\":\"\",\"72\":[\"147\"],\"67\":\"It was an amazing experience \\u2014 the level of knowledge from mentors and investors was beyond any events we have attended.\",\"69\":\"Founder, ZEX\",\"68\":\"Moataz Kotb\",\"71\":[\"230\"]}}', '2016-10-27 15:10:35', '2016-10-27 15:10:35', '72ac1fa4-4703-4d76-92d9-aed15c898372'),
 ('157', '7', '7', '1', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Who We Are\",\"slug\":\"who-we-are\",\"postDate\":1476724987,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"63\":\"Everyone at Rainmaking has been bitten by the entrepreneurial bug. We started in 2006 as a collective of serial entrepreneurs. Since then, we have grown into a global community of entrepreneurs, investors and ex-corporate executives. Driven to create something new, to make a difference, and have more fun doing it than should be allowed.  \\r\\n\\r\\nIf you love startups and are ok with getting some dirt under your fingernails, come join us. \",\"62\":\"\"}}', '2016-10-27 15:16:24', '2016-10-27 15:16:24', 'ec807421-6a3c-4c94-9433-523b52d25af8'),
 ('158', '169', '4', '15', 'en_us', '8', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"15\",\"title\":\"Making Copenhagen a Nordic FinTech Hub \",\"slug\":\"study-and-recommendations-for-making-copenhagen-a-nordic-fintech-hub\",\"postDate\":1477421940,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"70\":[\"218\"],\"47\":{\"170\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Mapping an Industry \",\"text\":\"In 2015 we were approached by a group of organizations including Finansforbundet, Danish Bankers Association, City of Copenhagen, DJ\\u00d8F, Nets, Saxo Bank, BEC, Tryg and CFIR for an opportunity to analyze and describe FinTech in Copenhagen.\\u00a0\\r\\n\\r\\nThe nine partners wanted to map the Danish FinTech environment, to benchmark Copenhagen against other cities and to identify initiatives that should be taken in order to develop and strengthen the FinTech ecosystem in Copenhagen.\\u00a0\",\"image\":[\"167\"],\"align\":\"left\"}},\"171\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"A 360 Degree View \",\"text\":\"Oxford Research and Rainmaking were chosen as consultants for the analysis. While Oxford Research has a deep knowledge of the Danish FinTech cluster from an institutional level; Rainmaking intimately knows the Danish startup scene and the international FinTech environment through our Startupbootcamp FinTech accelerators. Together we were able to partner to provide a holistic overview of the ecosystem, spanning both startup and corporate activity. \",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"172\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Thorough Investigation\",\"text\":\"We conducted five workshops focusing on different areas: research and education, investors, startups, regulation and public authorities, incubators\\/accelerators and corporates. It was important for the validity of the results that actors who know the FinTech ecosystem and the challenges for FinTech all had the opportunity to contribute, so, we involved over 250 people across all levels of the ecosystem, from executives to developers.\\u00a0\",\"backgroundColour\":\"white\"}},\"227\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Download the Summary Report Here\",\"text\":\"Recommendations for Making Copenhagen a Nordic FinTech Hub \",\"image\":[\"228\"],\"align\":\"right\"}},\"174\":{\"type\":\"videoBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"youtubeVideoId\":\"QD7STd0ZP88\"}}},\"80\":\"\",\"72\":[\"175\"],\"67\":\"It was an absolute privilege to take part in a study that could help position a relatively small city as a global hub\",\"69\":\"Partner at Rainmaking\",\"68\":\"Carsten K\\u00f8lbek\",\"71\":[\"229\"]}}', '2016-10-27 15:18:19', '2016-10-27 15:18:19', 'c4a7cbeb-6680-4932-ade6-20d8587d1f20'),
 ('159', '195', '4', '15', 'en_us', '5', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"15\",\"title\":\"How Lloyd\'s Banking Group Stays Ahead of FinTech Evolution\",\"slug\":\"how-lloyds-banking-group-stays-ahead-of-fintech-evolution\",\"postDate\":1477478580,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"70\":[\"178\"],\"47\":{\"196\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Partnering With Market Leaders\",\"text\":\"Since 2014 we have been helping to shape the global evolution of FinTech. Together with market leaders like MasterCard, Lloyds Banking Group, Santander, Thomson Reuters, PWC and Rabobank we run Startupbootcamp accelerator programs, design corporate innovation programs, and establish commercial connections between startups and established players.\",\"image\":[\"180\"],\"align\":\"left\"}},\"198\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"Each year we scout upwards of 3000 FinTech startups from across the globe. With accelerator programs in Singapore, London and New York, and 50+ FinTech events across almost every continent. \",\"image\":[\"179\"]}},\"199\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Early Access to Innovation\",\"text\":\"We select less than 1% of these startups for a Startupbootcamp cohort. This ensures our partners are collaborating with the best talent, often generating pilots, commercial partnerships and co-created solutions. Meanwhile, through the selection process itself, partners are exposed to evolving technology and business model trends at an early stage.  \",\"image\":[\"181\"],\"align\":\"right\"}},\"200\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Staying in Front of the Curve with Lloyd\'s \",\"text\":\"Lloyds Banking Group has been a partner on our Startupbootcamp FinTech program since 2014. The partnership came at a time when the bank was undertaking a large-scale digital transformation program, and presented an ideal platform to test new ideas and connect with the wider FinTech ecosystem. \",\"backgroundColour\":\"black\"}},\"201\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"\",\"text\":\"Lloyds\\u2019 goal is to scan the market for innovation and find new opportunities to provide better service to their customers. The relationship is beneficial for both parties: the FinTech startup has access to subject matter experts, launching customers and scarce assets like data sets. For Lloyds it is beneficial because they are able to learn about new technology, business models, see the results within the market and deduce important lessons to stay ahead and deliver value to their customers. \",\"image\":[\"182\"],\"align\":\"left\"}},\"202\":{\"type\":\"quoteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"The relationship with Startupbootcamp has been the first step towards collaborating with startups and to support our digital transformation agenda. By working with innovative partners we are able to deliver even better customer propositions and services.\",\"quoteName\":\"Claire Calmejane\",\"role\":\"Head of Innovation\",\"image\":[\"189\"]}},\"203\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"Keen to partner with Statupbootcamp\\u2019s portofolio companies, Lloyds has worked with alumni WoraPay \\u2013 a collaboration which is said to have saved Lloyds Banking Group employees 10,000 days of work. \",\"image\":[\"185\"]}},\"204\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"New Ways of Working\",\"text\":\"For Lloyds, collaborating with the FinTech sector also provides inspiring examples of agility and working practices that refresh Lloyd\\u2019s thinking and approach to delivering digital services. \\r\\n\\r\\nThe partnership gave Lloyds the chance to be involved in dedicated events such as FinTech Lounges and hackathons, presenting another opportunity to experience new ways of working.\\r\\n\",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"205\":{\"type\":\"imageBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"191\",\"193\",\"194\"]}}},\"80\":\"1\",\"72\":[\"179\"],\"67\":\"Our relationship with Rainmaking has given hundreds of our employees access to new tools and skillsets that they have used to become inspiring intrepreneurs inside Lloyds Banking Group.\\r\\n\",\"69\":\"Head of Innovation\",\"68\":\"Claire Calmejane\",\"71\":[\"189\"]}}', '2016-10-27 15:23:16', '2016-10-27 15:23:16', 'f747da8d-48eb-44d3-baf7-acaae99d6ca2'),
 ('160', '254', '8', '1', 'en_us', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Alex Farcet\",\"slug\":\"alex-farcet\",\"postDate\":1477582450,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"66\":\"\",\"1\":\"<p>Alex spent over twelve years in management positions with DHL and Deutsche Post until he had a realization that completely changed his perspective on taking risk and living with purpose. Since then, Alex&nbsp;has founded six companies, including Startupbootcamp, where he has personally helped hundreds of entrepreneurs launch their own businesses.<\\/p>\",\"65\":\"https:\\/\\/dk.linkedin.com\\/in\\/alexfarcet \"}}', '2016-10-27 15:34:11', '2016-10-27 15:34:11', '9f7dd430-dedc-4bbc-9d92-7e37653fad88'),
 ('161', '195', '4', '15', 'en_us', '6', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"15\",\"title\":\"How Lloyd\'s Banking Group Stays Ahead of FinTech Evolution\",\"slug\":\"how-lloyds-banking-group-stays-ahead-of-fintech-evolution\",\"postDate\":1477478580,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"70\":[\"178\"],\"47\":{\"196\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Partnering With Market Leaders\",\"text\":\"Since 2014 we have been helping to shape the global evolution of FinTech. Together with market leaders like MasterCard, Lloyds Banking Group, Santander, Thomson Reuters, PWC and Rabobank we run Startupbootcamp accelerator programs, design corporate innovation programs, and establish commercial connections between startups and established players.\",\"image\":[\"180\"],\"align\":\"left\"}},\"198\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"Each year we scout upwards of 3000 FinTech startups from across the globe. With accelerator programs in Singapore, London and New York, and 50+ FinTech events across almost every continent. \",\"image\":[\"179\"]}},\"199\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Early Access to Innovation\",\"text\":\"We select less than 1% of these startups for a Startupbootcamp cohort. This ensures our partners are collaborating with the best talent, often generating pilots, commercial partnerships and co-created solutions. Meanwhile, through the selection process itself, partners are exposed to evolving technology and business model trends at an early stage.  \",\"image\":[\"181\"],\"align\":\"right\"}},\"200\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Staying in Front of the Curve with Lloyd\'s \",\"text\":\"Lloyds Banking Group has been a partner on our Startupbootcamp FinTech program since 2014. The partnership came at a time when the bank was undertaking a large-scale digital transformation program, and presented an ideal platform to test new ideas and connect with the wider FinTech ecosystem. \",\"backgroundColour\":\"black\"}},\"201\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"\",\"text\":\"Lloyds\\u2019 goal is to scan the market for innovation and find new opportunities to provide better service to their customers. The relationship is beneficial for both parties: the FinTech startup has access to subject matter experts, launching customers and scarce assets like data sets. For Lloyds it is beneficial because they are able to learn about new technology, business models, see the results within the market and deduce important lessons to stay ahead and deliver value to their customers. \",\"image\":[\"182\"],\"align\":\"left\"}},\"202\":{\"type\":\"quoteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"The relationship with Startupbootcamp has been the first step towards collaborating with startups and to support our digital transformation agenda. By working with innovative partners we are able to deliver even better customer propositions and services.\",\"quoteName\":\"Claire Calmejane\",\"role\":\"Head of Innovation\",\"image\":[\"189\"]}},\"203\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"Collaborating with Startupbootcamp alumni WoraPay \\u2013 is said to have saved Lloyds Banking Group employees 10,000 days of work. \",\"image\":[\"185\"]}},\"204\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"New Ways of Working\",\"text\":\"For Lloyds, collaborating with the FinTech sector also provides inspiring examples of agility and working practices that refresh Lloyd\\u2019s thinking and approach to delivering digital services. \\r\\n\\r\\nThe partnership gave Lloyds the chance to be involved in dedicated events such as FinTech Lounges and hackathons, presenting another opportunity to experience new ways of working.\\r\\n\",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"205\":{\"type\":\"imageBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"191\",\"193\",\"194\"]}}},\"80\":\"1\",\"72\":[\"179\"],\"67\":\"Our relationship with Rainmaking has given hundreds of our employees access to new tools and skillsets that they have used to become inspiring intrepreneurs inside Lloyds Banking Group.\\r\\n\",\"69\":\"Head of Innovation\",\"68\":\"Claire Calmejane\",\"71\":[\"189\"]}}', '2016-10-27 15:34:33', '2016-10-27 15:34:33', '834bcefa-677c-47af-b4f1-6cb3593d8143'),
 ('162', '255', '8', '1', 'en_us', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Nektarios Liolios:\",\"slug\":\"nektarios-liolios\",\"postDate\":1477582915,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"66\":\"\",\"1\":\"<p>Nektarios has over eleven years\\u2019&nbsp;experience in the banking and financial sector. While working for SWIFT\\u2019s&nbsp;Innotribe he&nbsp;facilitated interactions between startups and financial institutions. Nektarios continues this today,&nbsp;leading Startupbootcamp FinTech & InsurTech.<\\/p>\",\"65\":\"https:\\/\\/uk.linkedin.com\\/in\\/nekliolios\"}}', '2016-10-27 15:41:57', '2016-10-27 15:41:57', 'be9a5258-159a-40f8-9da4-0b22082d1f34'),
 ('163', '255', '8', '1', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"8\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Nektarios Liolios\",\"slug\":\"nektarios-liolios\",\"postDate\":1477582860,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"66\":\"\",\"1\":\"<p>Nektarios has over eleven years\\u2019&nbsp;experience in the banking and financial sector. While working for SWIFT\\u2019s&nbsp;Innotribe he&nbsp;facilitated interactions between startups and financial institutions. Nektarios continues this today,&nbsp;leading Startupbootcamp FinTech & InsurTech.<\\/p>\",\"65\":\"https:\\/\\/uk.linkedin.com\\/in\\/nekliolios\",\"81\":\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/nekliolios\"}}', '2016-10-27 15:42:29', '2016-10-27 15:42:29', '9fa6139d-7c2b-41ec-8739-0aae72481641'),
 ('164', '254', '8', '1', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"8\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Alex Farcet\",\"slug\":\"alex-farcet\",\"postDate\":1477582440,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"66\":\"\",\"1\":\"<p>Alex spent over twelve years in management positions with DHL and Deutsche Post until he had a realization that completely changed his perspective on taking risk and living with purpose. Since then, Alex&nbsp;has founded six companies, including Startupbootcamp, where he has personally helped hundreds of entrepreneurs launch their own businesses.<\\/p>\",\"65\":\"https:\\/\\/dk.linkedin.com\\/in\\/alexfarcet \",\"82\":[\"257\"],\"81\":\"\"}}', '2016-10-27 15:53:18', '2016-10-27 15:53:18', 'c4eee2c7-e718-4eda-b744-d53bbb0b5483'),
 ('165', '255', '8', '1', 'en_us', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"8\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Nektarios Liolios\",\"slug\":\"nektarios-liolios\",\"postDate\":1477582860,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"66\":\"\",\"1\":\"<p>Nektarios has over eleven years\\u2019&nbsp;experience in the banking and financial sector. While working for SWIFT\\u2019s&nbsp;Innotribe he&nbsp;facilitated interactions between startups and financial institutions. Nektarios continues this today,&nbsp;leading Startupbootcamp FinTech & InsurTech.<\\/p>\",\"65\":\"https:\\/\\/uk.linkedin.com\\/in\\/nekliolios\",\"82\":[\"258\"],\"81\":\"https:\\/\\/twitter.com\\/nekliolios\"}}', '2016-10-27 15:55:22', '2016-10-27 15:55:22', 'c9b5b3f8-84ab-4c51-820f-6b40ad3071dd'),
 ('166', '24', '4', '15', 'en_us', '23', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"15\",\"title\":\"How Danske Bank Engages with Over 600 Startups\",\"slug\":\"how-danske-bank-is-making-a-splash-in-the-startup-world\",\"postDate\":1477327740,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"70\":[\"23\"],\"47\":{\"42\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"We partnered with Danske Bank to create TheHub.dk, a platform that aims to relieve the pains of Danish startups and provide a platform for Danske Bank to engage with the startup ecosystem. \",\"image\":[\"37\"]}},\"43\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Participating in the Future \",\"text\":\"Danske Bank came to us in the Fall of 2015 with an exciting challenge: to create and run a project that would add value to Danish startups and accelerate the growth of early stage companies.\\u00a0\\r\\n\\r\\nDanske Bank wanted to test new forms of engagement with emerging businesses. By actively participating in the Danish startup ecosystem, they gain early insights into new technologies and business models that could impact their business in the future.\\r\\n\\r\\nBy supporting startups at an early stage, helping them succeed and grow, Danske Bank also creates a wider stream of potential future customers.\",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"44\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"An Online Recruiting Platform, Community and Resource Center \",\"text\":\"After over 100 founder interviews, we found three major pain points faced by Danish startups: \\r\\n\\r\\n1. Recruitment: lack of a nationwide, startup focused job board \\r\\n\\r\\n2. Funding: navigating the overwhelming number of investors and funding options to find the right choice\\r\\n\\r\\n3. Knowledge Sharing: capitalizing on the experience of successful founders to accelerate progress\\r\\n\\r\\nWith these three problems in mind, we created The Hub.\\r\\n\",\"image\":[\"247\"],\"align\":\"left\"}},\"249\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"With these three problems in mind, we created The Hub.\",\"image\":\"\"}},\"90\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Top Tech Talent\",\"text\":\"Targeting recruitment first, we built a job board tailored specifically to startups. \\r\\n\\r\\nWe found that startups rely on their own networks and traditional job boards for hiring. But they were missing something fit for purpose. Specifically for entrepreneurs. Targeting job seekers interested in joining startups.\\r\\n\\r\\nWe\\u2019ve now created over 550 startup profiles and see over 11000 weekly visits, converting to 600 weekly applications. This is paired with great feedback from both startups and applicants using the site. \",\"backgroundColour\":\"black\"}},\"120\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"We\\u2019ve now created over 550 startup profiles and see over 11000 weekly visits, converting to 600 weekly applications.\",\"image\":[\"39\"]}},\"46\":{\"type\":\"quoteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"\\\"We received far more applications through the Hub compared to elsewhere. All the applicants were relevant and part of our target group. For those reasons, I would recommend the Hub (and have already done it)\\\"\",\"quoteName\":\"Happy Hub User\",\"role\":\"\",\"image\":[\"259\"]}},\"47\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Connection With Investors \",\"text\":\"To help navigate the funding options available to Danish startups, our next solution was to create a tool which could match startups with the most relevant options for them, based on their industry, experience, level of maturity and team size. This included profiles of the top 50 investors in Denmark.\",\"image\":[\"39\"],\"align\":\"right\"}},\"48\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Access to Expert Knowledge\",\"text\":\"Knowledge sharing posed the greatest challenge. The majority of the information startups need is topical, specific to their industry, stage and product. \\r\\n\\r\\nThe Hub therefore needed to address the need for both startup specific, and generic content. To achieve this, we\\u2019ve started to develop a mentor matching scheme to pair startups with relevant advisors. \\r\\n\\r\\nMeanwhile, we\\u2019ve also developed a number of tools to share best practices around some of the steps almost all startups follow.  From raising funds to gaining the very first customers.\",\"backgroundColour\":\"black\"}},\"49\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Widening The Hub\\u2019s Reach\",\"text\":\"Today, the Hub is the largest startup recruitment site in Denmark. And, we\\u2019re now applying what we\\u2019ve learned across the Nordics, launching Hubs in Norway and Sweden, opening up opportunities for cross-country applications in markets where Danske Bank is most active.\",\"image\":[\"251\"],\"align\":\"left\"}},\"166\":{\"type\":\"videoBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"youtubeVideoId\":\"V3RTOLI33Q0\"}}},\"80\":\"1\",\"72\":[\"36\"],\"67\":\"We have partnered with Rainmaking because of their strong foothold in the global startup ecosystem, and their impressive ability to launch and grow new platforms and services at high speed\",\"69\":\"Head of Business Innovation\",\"68\":\"Klavs Hjort\",\"71\":[\"22\"]}}', '2016-10-27 15:59:31', '2016-10-27 15:59:31', '61160474-ce96-4315-aeb5-32b80623414d'),
