 ('190', '246', '3', '15', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"15\",\"title\":\"The Rainmaking Sessions - Disruptive InsurTech: From now to 2030\",\"slug\":\"the-rainmaking-sessions-disruptive-insurtech-from-now-to-2030\",\"postDate\":1477571040,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"25\":\"1 St. Katherine\'s Way, London, E1W 1UN\",\"1\":\"<p>For years FinTech has dominating with news of investments, advancements and innovation. However, the industry on everyone\\u2019s radar for 2016 is insurance. In order to examine these developments, Rainmaking Innovations, in association with Startupbootcamp InsurTech, invite you to an exclusive breakfast roundtable event looking at digital disruption in insurance.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Disruptive InsurTech: From now to 2030 - What will your path to success be?<\\/em>&nbsp;will be an interactive, think tank style roundtable where you can hear from industry experts to debate and discuss the current state of the industry as well as future trends with your peers.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You will hear from:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul><li>Sabine VanderLinden, MD Startupbootcamp InsurTech<\\/li><li>Carolina Vicente,&nbsp;Director of Digital Marketing, Google<\\/li><li>Moderated by: Liz Lumley, Rainmaking Innovation<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Please join us at the Rainmaking Loft to be a part of the first of a series of thought provoking Rainmaking Sessions looking at innovation and disruptive trends.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul><li>When:&nbsp;28 October 2016<\\/li><li>Where:&nbsp;The Rainmaking Loft, 1 St Katherine\\u2019s Way, London E1W 4UN<\\/li><li>Agenda:<\\/li><li>9:00 - Arrival at loft for coffee<\\/li><li>9:15 - Buffet style breakfast served<\\/li><li>9:45 - Welcome and talks begin<\\/li><li>10:15 - Moderated Roundtable starts<\\/li><li>11:30 - Breakfast Roundtable ends<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Spaces are limited, so please RSVP&nbsp;for your chance to be a part of this special event.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"23\":\"https:\\/\\/www.eventbrite.co.uk\\/e\\/disruptive-insurtech-from-now-to-2030-registration-26699864012\",\"73\":[\"182\"],\"24\":\"Rainmaking Loft - London\",\"26\":{\"date\":\"10\\/28\\/2016\",\"time\":\"9:00 AM\"}}}', '2016-10-28 10:22:43', '2016-10-28 10:22:43', '2d32b8c2-c8a5-47d5-a5ff-189db48f2ac6'),
