 ('203', '254', '8', '15', 'en_us', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"8\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Alex Farcet\",\"slug\":\"alex-farcet\",\"postDate\":1477582440,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"66\":\"\",\"1\":\"<p>Alex spent over twelve years in management positions with DHL and Deutsche Post until he had a realization that completely changed his perspective on taking risk and living with purpose. Since then, Alex&nbsp;has founded six companies, including Startupbootcamp, where he has personally helped hundreds of entrepreneurs launch their own businesses.<\\/p>\",\"65\":\"https:\\/\\/dk.linkedin.com\\/in\\/alexfarcet \",\"82\":[\"279\"],\"81\":\"\"}}', '2016-10-28 13:48:15', '2016-10-28 13:48:15', '764f002e-15f8-4aeb-b0d0-70b36405434b'),
