\"header\":\"Access to Expert Knowledge\",\"text\":\"Knowledge sharing posed the greatest challenge. The majority of the information startups need is topical, specific to their industry, stage and product. \\r\\n\\r\\nThe Hub therefore needed to address the need for both startup specific, and generic content. To achieve this, we\\u2019ve started to develop a mentor matching scheme to pair startups with relevant advisors. \\r\\n\\r\\nMeanwhile, we\\u2019ve also developed a number of tools to share best practices around some of the steps almost all startups follow.  From raising funds to gaining the very first customers.\",\"backgroundColour\":\"black\"}},\"49\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Widening The Hub\\u2019s Reach\",\"text\":\"Today, the Hub is the largest startup recruitment site in Denmark. And, we\\u2019re now applying what we\\u2019ve learned across the Nordics, launching Hubs in Norway and Sweden, opening up opportunities for cross-country applications in markets where Danske Bank is most active.\",\"image\":[\"251\"],\"align\":\"left\"}},\"166\":{\"type\":\"videoBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"youtubeVideoId\":\"V3RTOLI33Q0\"}}},\"80\":\"1\",\"72\":[\"36\"],\"67\":\"We have partnered with Rainmaking because of their strong foothold in the global startup ecosystem, and their impressive ability to launch and grow new platforms and services at high speed\",\"69\":\"Head of Business Innovation\",\"68\":\"Klavs Hjort\",\"71\":[\"22\"]}}', '2016-11-01 10:38:59', '2016-11-01 10:38:59', '6779bee0-6d5d-4515-a12f-74f5db8512cf'),
 ('277', '8', '9', '15', 'en_us', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Companies\",\"slug\":\"companies\",\"postDate\":1476725045,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>Creating companies and bringing them to market is our first love. Together, we\\u2019ve built over 25 of our own startups, achieved 5 notable exits and participated in more than 350 investments. Here are just a few active companies that we have built.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"73\":[\"20\"],\"62\":\"25 startups, 5 exits, 350+ investments\"}}', '2016-11-01 10:50:17', '2016-11-01 10:50:17', 'c399aa35-36be-45b8-8635-9cd5c7008911'),
 ('278', '9', '10', '15', 'en_us', '5', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Accelerator\",\"slug\":\"accelerator\",\"postDate\":1476725058,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>Since we co-founded Startupbootcamp in 2006, it\\u2019s become one of the world\\u2019s leading, industry specific accelerator programs, driving collaboration between startups and established players across entire ecosystems. To date we have 16 programs in 13 cities across the globe with a presence in every major geography. Startups come to us looking for the right partners, investors and mentors to take the next step forward. Our corporate partners come to us to find the next big thing and gain access to a global network.<\\/p>\",\"73\":[\"18\"],\"62\":\"Startupbootcamp\"}}', '2016-11-01 10:50:41', '2016-11-01 10:50:41', '6ef16f82-c0e2-43f2-8224-4d899c124b77'),
