ns. We love results not presentations. Actions not words. \\r\\n\\r\\nJust see for yourself.\",\"77\":[\"19\"],\"5\":\"We created Rainmaking Loft coworking spaces. Serving over 1,000 entrepreneurs in London, Berlin and Copenhagen.\"}}', '2016-11-14 18:00:10', '2016-11-14 18:00:10', 'fc01a837-c170-4d51-8a9d-6e58c3e544e5'),
