 ('329', '24', '4', '15', 'en_us', '27', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"15\",\"title\":\"Engaging Over 600 Startups with Danske Bank \",\"slug\":\"how-danske-bank-is-making-a-splash-in-the-startup-world\",\"postDate\":1477327740,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"70\":[\"23\"],\"91\":\"\",\"47\":{\"42\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"We partnered with Danske Bank to create TheHub.dk, a platform that aims to relieve the pains of Danish startups and provide a platform for Danske Bank to engage with the startup ecosystem. \",\"image\":[\"37\"]}},\"43\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Participating in the Future \",\"text\":\"<p>Danske Bank came to us in the Fall of 2015 with an exciting challenge: to create and run a project that would add value to Danish startups and accelerate the growth of early stage companies.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Danske Bank wanted to test new forms of engagement with emerging businesses. By actively participating in the Danish startup ecosystem, they gain early insights into new technologies and business models that could impact their business in the future.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>By supporting startups at an early stage, helping them succeed and grow, Danske Bank also creates a wider stream of potential future customers.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"44\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"An Online Recruiting Platform, Community and Resource Center \",\"text\":\"<p>After over 100 founder interviews, we found three major pain points faced by Danish startups: <\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>1. Recruitment: lack of a nationwide, startup focused job board <\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>2. Funding: navigating the overwhelming number of investors and funding options to find the right choice<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>3. Knowledge Sharing: capitalizing on the experience of successful founders to accelerate progress<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>With these three problems in mind, we created The Hub.<\\/p>\",\"image\":[\"247\"],\"align\":\"left\"}},\"249\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"With these three problems in mind, we created The Hub.\",\"image\":[\"36\"]}},\"90\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Top Tech Talent\",\"text\":\"<p>Targeting recruitment first, we built a job board tailored specifically to startups. <\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We found that startups rely on their own networks and traditional job boards for hiring. But they were missing something fit for purpose. Specifically for entrepreneurs. Targeting job seekers interested in joining startups.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We\\u2019ve now created over 550 startup profiles and see over 11000 weekly visits, converting to 600 weekly applications. This is paired with great feedback from both startups and applicants using the site.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColour\":\"black\"}},\"120\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"We\\u2019ve now created over 550 startup profiles and see over 11000 weekly visits, converting to 600 weekly applications.\",\"image\":[\"39\"]}},\"46\":{\"type\":\"quoteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"\\\"We received far more applications through the Hub compared to elsewhere. All the applicants were relevant and part of our target group. For those reasons, I would recommend the Hub (and have already done it)\\\"\",\"quoteName\":\"Happy Hub User\",\"role\":\"\",\"image\":[\"259\"]}},\"47\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Connection With Investors \",\"text\":\"<p>To help navigate the funding options available to Danish startups, our next solution was to create a tool which could match startups with the most relevant options for them, based on their industry, experience, level of maturity and team size. This included profiles of the top 50 investors in Denmark.<\\/p>\",\"image\":[\"39\"],\"align\":\"right\"}},\"48\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Access to Expert Knowledge\",\"text\":\"<p>Knowledge sharing posed the greatest challenge. The majority of the information startups need is topical, specific to their industry, stage and product. <\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The Hub therefore needed to address the need for both startup specific, and generic content. To achieve this, we\\u2019ve started to develop a mentor matching scheme to pair startups with relevant advisors. <\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Meanwhile, we\\u2019ve also developed a number of tools to share best practices around some of the steps almost all startups follow. From raising funds to gaining the very first customers.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColour\":\"black\"}},\"49\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Widening The Hub\\u2019s Reach\",\"text\":\"<p>Today, the Hub is the largest startup recruitment site in Denmark. And, we\\u2019re now applying what we\\u2019ve learned across the Nordics, launching Hubs in Norway and Sweden, opening up opportunities for cross-country applications in markets where Danske Bank is most active.<\\/p>\",\"image\":[\"251\"],\"align\":\"left\"}},\"166\":{\"type\":\"videoBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"youtubeVideoId\":\"V3RTOLI33Q0\"}}},\"80\":\"1\",\"72\":[\"36\"],\"100\":\"\",\"99\":\"\",\"67\":\"We have partnered with Rainmaking because of their strong foothold in the global startup ecosystem, and their impressive ability to launch and grow new platforms and services at high speed\",\"69\":\"Head of Business Innovation\",\"68\":\"Klavs Hjort\",\"71\":[\"22\"]}}', '2016-11-15 10:47:58', '2016-11-15 10:47:58', '7ac63a91-36d3-458f-8a69-7b6b475b5ded'),
 ('330', '86', '4', '15', 'en_us', '11', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"15\",\"title\":\"Promoting Trade and Cooperation Between the EU and GCC\",\"slug\":\"bolstering-trade-investment-and-cooperation-between-the-eu-and-gcc\",\"postDate\":1477400400,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"70\":[\"218\"],\"91\":\"\",\"47\":{\"87\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Collaboration Between SME\'s, Startups, and Corporates\",\"text\":\"<p>Following the success of our ecosystem development work in the MENA regions, we were trusted to co-create the 2015 EU-GCC program. A pilot initiative intended to promote trade between the EU and GCC as well as increase cooperation between corporates, SME\\u2019s and startups.<\\/p><p>We partnered with The Danish Confederation of Industry, Business Europe, and the Federation of Gulf Cooperation Council Chambers (\\u2018GCC\\u2019) to design and deliver this project, funded by the EU Commission.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"88\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Optimizing Relations\",\"text\":\"<p>Despite a past characterized by sociopolitical challenges, the GCC and EU are increasingly reliant on each other for trade and investment. The GCC stands as the fifth top trading partner with the EU and accounts for over \\u20ac100 Billion in EU goods exports.<\\/p><p>While trade is increasing steadily year over year, the majority is still based on mineral fuels and industrial products.<\\/p>\",\"image\":[\"84\"],\"align\":\"left\"}},\"89\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"Our challenge was to promote trade bilaterally in underrepresented areas such as services and technology, while also increasing collaboration in the development of new innovations.\",\"image\":[\"85\"]}},\"95\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Building on Existing Platforms\",\"text\":\"<p>Having already built up a strong local presence in the GCC region and Europe, and proven the success of our workshop format through our Startup MENA Program, we were able to draw on our existing network of engaged corporates and ecosystem players to design a series of premium workshops and match-making events.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColour\":\"white\"}},\"96\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"24 Events in 10 Countries \",\"text\":\"<p>Over the course of 2015 we ran 24 events across 10 countries. And, successfully highlighted disruptive startups from the GCC, training entrepreneurs, matching corporates to startups for commercial partnerships, and promoting the Gulf as a market to EU startups and SMEs.<\\/p>\",\"image\":[\"91\"],\"align\":\"right\"}},\"97\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"We Designed and Delivered:\",\"text\":\"<ul><li>Intensive workshops in Kuwait City, Doha, Muscat, Dubai, Manama, Jeddah, London, Berlin, Brussels and Rome<\\/li><li>Match-making events in London and Dubai<\\/li><li>An international pitch challenge touring Kuwait, Bahrain, UAE, Qatar, Saudi Arabia and Oman<\\/li><li>An online matchmaking portal: EU-GCC Connect<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"98\":{\"type\":\"imageBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"92\",\"93\"]}},\"99\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Continued Operation\",\"text\":\"<p>Building on the success of the EU-GCC program in 2015, the initiative will continue to run until 2018.<\\/p><p>The data and reports generated by Rainmaking will be used as the bedrock of further efforts to increase trade and investment across various industries.<\\/p><p><span><\\/span>The Danish Confederation of Industry, Business Europe, and the Federation of Gulf Cooperation Council Chambers are all driven to to progress further; forging closer links, removing regulatory barriers, and increasing trade.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColour\":\"black\"}}},\"80\":\"\",\"72\":[\"94\"],\"100\":\"Get in touch\",\"99\":\"Ready to make a splash?\",\"67\":\"It was an absolutely amazing experience to help talented entrepreneurs while simultaneously increasing international cooperation.\",\"69\":\"Rainmaking Partner\",\"68\":\"Jakob Kistorp\",\"71\":[\"214\"]}}', '2016-11-15 10:51:08', '2016-11-15 10:51:08', 'f811f330-4a0e-45ad-8bd3-e7aa953412ec'),
