ree problems in mind, we created The Hub.<\\/p>\",\"image\":[\"247\"],\"align\":\"left\"}},\"249\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"With these three problems in mind, we created The Hub.\",\"image\":[\"36\"]}},\"90\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Top Tech Talent\",\"text\":\"<p>Targeting recruitment first, we built a job board tailored specifically to startups.<\\/p><p>We found that startups rely on their own networks and traditional job boards for hiring. But they were missing something fit for purpose. Specifically for entrepreneurs. Targeting job seekers interested in joining startups.<\\/p><p><span><\\/span>We\\u2019ve now created over 550 startup profiles and see over 11000 weekly visits, converting to 600 weekly applications. This is paired with great feedback from both startups and applicants using the site.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColour\":\"black\"}},\"120\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"We\\u2019ve now created over 550 startup profiles and see over 11000 weekly visits, converting to 600 weekly applications.\",\"image\":[\"39\"]}},\"46\":{\"type\":\"quoteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"\\\"We received far more applications through the Hub compared to elsewhere. All the applicants were relevant and part of our target group. For those reasons, I would recommend the Hub (and have already done it)\\\"\",\"quoteName\":\"Happy Hub User\",\"role\":\"\",\"image\":[\"259\"]}},\"47\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Connection With Investors \",\"text\":\"<p>To help navigate the funding options available to Danish startups, our next solution was to create a tool which could match startups with the most relevant options for them, based on their industry, experience, level of maturity and team size. This included profiles of the top 50 investors in Denmark.<\\/p>\",\"image\":[\"39\"],\"align\":\"right\"}},\"48\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Access to Expert Knowledge\",\"text\":\"<p>Knowledge sharing posed the greatest challenge. The majority of the information startups need is topical, specific to their industry, stage and product.<\\/p><p>The Hub therefore needed to address the need for both startup specific, and generic content. To achieve this, we\\u2019ve started to develop a mentor matching scheme to pair startups with relevant advisors.<\\/p><p><span><\\/span>Meanwhile, we\\u2019ve also developed a number of tools to share best practices around some of the steps almost all startups follow. From raising funds to gaining the very first customers.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColour\":\"black\"}},\"49\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Widening The Hub\\u2019s Reach\",\"text\":\"<p>Today, the Hub is the largest startup recruitment site in Denmark. And, we\\u2019re now applying what we\\u2019ve learned across the Nordics, launching Hubs in Norway and Sweden, opening up opportunities for cross-country applications in markets where Danske Bank is most active.<\\/p>\",\"image\":[\"251\"],\"align\":\"left\"}},\"166\":{\"type\":\"videoBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"youtubeVideoId\":\"V3RTOLI33Q0\"}}},\"80\":\"1\",\"72\":[\"36\"],\"100\":\"Get in touch\",\"99\":\"Want to launch digital products, startup style?\",\"67\":\"We have partnered with Rainmaking because of their strong foothold in the global startup ecosystem, and their impressive ability to launch and grow new platforms and services at high speed\",\"69\":\"Head of Business Innovation\",\"68\":\"Klavs Hjort\",\"71\":[\"22\"]}}', '2016-11-15 11:11:09', '2016-11-15 11:11:09', 'b3a4342c-b7fc-4f26-93e1-0224e8a402b9'),
 ('332', '57', '4', '15', 'en_us', '12', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"15\",\"title\":\"Finding the Future of Transportation for Daimler\",\"slug\":\"finding-the-future-of-transportation-for-daimler\",\"postDate\":1477393440,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"70\":[\"51\"],\"91\":\"\",\"47\":{\"58\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Finding the Driving Edge of Startup Talent\",\"text\":\"<p>Daimler, a partner of Startupbootcamp Smart Transportation, owner of Mercedes Benz and the largest commercial vehicle manufacturer in the world, came to us looking for startups that could help them gain an edge against competition and stay up to date on emerging technology.<\\/p><p>We sourced over 1,000 startups from across 18 countries and identified a number of forces that are shaping the future of transportation and mobility.<\\/p>\",\"image\":[\"50\"],\"align\":\"left\"}},\"252\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"\\\"We sourced over 1,000 startups from across 18 countries and identified a number of forces that are shaping the future of transportation and mobility.\\\"\",\"image\":\"\"}},\"59\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Staying In the Fast Lane\",\"text\":\"<p>As cars have become connected, electric and autonomous, Daimler has recognized that they must identify new innovations early in order to stay at the forefront of current technological advancements.<\\/p><p>Our challenge was to find the next generation of startups that could help Daimler overtake their competition.<\\/p><p><span><\\/span>With this in mind, Daimler asked us to source startup talent, and identify trends that are driving innovation within the smart mobility space.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"60\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"\\u00a1Hola Brazil!\",\"text\":\"<p>Our sourcing team screened startups from around the globe. And, identified the most interesting startups for Daimler.<\\/p><p>Beginning with a world wide scope, we quickly identified Europe and Brazil as exciting areas for new talent.<\\/p><p><span><\\/span>Responding to global trends, we saw that Brazil\\u2019s growth had opened up new markets and created untapped opportunities for startups. In particular, urbanization and rapid population growth present problems that startups are actively finding innovative solutions to. This led us to a new hotbed of talent that was generally underrepresented in mainstream sources.<\\/p>\",\"image\":[\"52\"],\"align\":\"right\"}},\"61\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"\\\"Beginning with a world wide scope, we quickly identified Europe and Brazil as exciting areas for new talent.\\\"\",\"image\":[\"212\"]}},\"62\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Getting the Whole Picture\",\"text\":\"<p>At the end of the two month sourcing period we had:<\\/p><ul><li>Sourced startups from 87 data sources<\\/li><li>Covered 18 countries<\\/li><li>Reviewed 1759 startups<\\/li><li>Selected 326 startups for further review<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\",\"backgroundColour\":\"black\"}},\"63\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Delivering Startups, Trends, and Actionable Intel\",\"text\":\"<p>Our internal panel reviewed and assessed these startups, refining the selection to a top 40. These were presented back to Daimler alongside a trend report capturing industry insights, further highlighting opportunities for engagement within the startup world.<\\/p><p>Today Daimler remains actively involved in the startup ecosystem, as a partner in our Smart Transportation & Energy Startupbootcamp and continues to pursue new innovations.<\\/p>\",\"image\":[\"54\"],\"align\":\"right\"}}},\"80\":\"1\",\"72\":[\"262\"],\"100\":\"Get in touch\",\"99\":\"Want to keep an eye on developing trends?\",\"67\":\"Partnering with Startupbootcamp will accelerate our access to innovation and will plug us into an impressive community of alumni, mentors and investors.\",\"69\":\"Senior Manager, Business Innovation\",\"68\":\"Dr. Frank Spennemann\",\"71\":[\"263\"]}}', '2016-11-15 11:13:13', '2016-11-15 11:13:13', 'e026cb01-d922-43c8-b0ac-a2937c8d2e8b'),
 ('333', '108', '4', '15', 'en_us', '6', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"15\",\"title\":\"From Idea to Business: Employee Powered Innovation at Majid Al Futtaim\",\"slug\":\"from-idea-to-business-employee-powered-innovation-at-majid-al-futtaim\",\"postDate\":1477406580,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"70\":[\"106\"],\"91\":\"\",\"47\":{\"109\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"A three day hackathon followed by an intensive five day program, transforming ideas into viable businesses.\",\"image\":[\"100\"]}},\"110\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Responding To Changing Times\",\"text\":\"<p>Majid Al Futtaim runs Malls and Carrefour hypermarkets across the Middle East, North Africa and Central Asia including the Mall of the Emirates, famous for its indoor ski slope.&nbsp;<\\/p><p>Their large physical footprint has given them a distinctive advantage in the retail market, however, with consumer behaviors evolving towards an increasingly digital experience, Majid Al Futtaim wanted to explore how they could be more innovative; both in their customer experiences, and their ways of working.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"111\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"48 Hours to Create a New Experience for Dubai\",\"text\":\"<p>As the first phase of the \\u201cNext Great Moment\\u201d challenge, we created a two day hackathon. This inspired Majid Al Futtaim\\u2019s employees to refine internal ideas for new and innovative products and services in just 48 hours.<\\/p><p>In addition to generating new and innovative ideas, the event gave employees direct experience applying a more entrepreneurial mindset. It also served to create both internal and external excitement around Majid Al Futtaim\'s innovative approach.<\\/p>\",\"image\":[\"101\"],\"align\":\"left\"}},\"112\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"\",\"text\":\"<p>From over 1300 applications, 83 talented individuals were selected to attend this intensive experience. By bringing together employees from across the company, we reinforced the importance of collaboration to drive innovation and escape the natural silos of the organization.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"113\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Thinking Big\",\"text\":\"<p>Each attendee had just 60 seconds to pitch their idea, before teams formed around the 10 most popular concepts.<\\/p><p>They then had just two days to test and evolve their value proposition through customer interviews, and industry research. Finally, they distilled their updated business idea into a 3 minute pitch.<\\/p><p><span><\\/span>Throughout the weekend, teams were exposed to new methodologies; an intensive series of exercises and workshops which encouraged attendees to \\u201cThink Big\\u201d, introducing them to Global Trends to further inspire their efforts.<\\/p>\",\"image\":[\"102\"],\"align\":\"right\"}},\"114\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"\\\"From over 1300 applications, 83 talented individuals were selected to attend this intensive experience.\\\"\",\"image\":[\"100\"]}},\"115\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Making the Most of Every Minute\",\"text\":\"<p>We held networking events and icebreakers to encourage teams to utilize the event to meet as many colleagues and industry experts as possible.<\\/p><p>Expert pitch trainers taught the teams to present with impact, polishing their pitches, and honing presentation skills.<\\/p><p><span><\\/span>Meanwhile, serial entrepreneurs and thought leaders were on hand to offer the teams mentoring and further training, inspiring participants with startup approaches to propel them forward.<\\/p>\",\"image\":[\"103\"],\"align\":\"right\"}},\"116\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Ideas to Move You: From Dubai to London\",\"text\":\"<p>In this supportive, yet challenging, environment, ideas evolved rapidly. <br>A wide range of concepts were developed throughout this process; offering MAF a choice of radically innovative solutions, alongside those which could be quickly implemented.<\\/p><p>Two of the most exciting ideas won the prize of 5 weeks in London with Rainmaking. Here, we created an immersive Pop-Up Lab which pushed their business models, teamwork and delivery even further.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"117\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"\\\"Two of the most exciting ideas won the prize of 5 weeks in London with Rainmaking.\\\"\",\"image\":[\"104\"]}},\"176\":{\"type\":\"videoBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"youtubeVideoId\":\"yEzjhZOcJAg\"}},\"118\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"New Skills and New Business\",\"text\":\"<p>These teams left the Pop-Up Lab with a new appreciation of Lean Startup approaches, experience conducting customer interviews, and greater insight into working collaboratively in a newly formed team. Equipped with new ways of approaching problems and understanding customer needs they are more able to create meaningful change to MAF\'s business.<\\/p>\",\"image\":[\"105\"],\"align\":\"left\"}}},\"80\":\"\",\"72\":[\"100\"],\"100\":\"Get in touch\",\"99\":\"Want to empower your teams to innovate?\",\"67\":\"The Innovation Challenge provides a unique opportunity for us to foster a culture of innovation amongst our people.\",\"69\":\"CEO, MAF Ventures\",\"68\":\"Galal Ismail\",\"71\":[\"107\"]}}', '2016-11-15 11:14:43', '2016-11-15 11:14:43', 'd67c27c1-8a35-4a3e-8951-9064a2efc8f5'),
 ('334', '129', '4', '15', 'en_us', '6', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"15\",\"title\":\"Sourcing Europe\'s Best EdTech Startups for Collaboration With Sanoma\",\"slug\":\"sourcing-europes-best-edtech-startups-for-collaboration-with-sanoma\",\"postDate\":1477412460,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"70\":[\"127\"],\"91\":\"\",\"47\":{\"130\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Strategic Deal Flow: A Win-Win\",\"text\":\"<p>For this project we were entrusted with finding hopeful EdTech startups with the potential to grow their business together with Sanoma, the Nordic region\\u2019s leading media and learning company.<\\/p><p>Promising startups were invited to participate in the \\u201cSanoma Startup Challenge - the future of learning,\\u201d an event which we designed and delivered to discover promising startup talent.<\\/p>\",\"image\":[\"122\"],\"align\":\"left\"}},\"131\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"The Future of Learning\",\"text\":\"<p>Sanoma Ventures came to us looking for ways to find high quality deal flow for their newly formed corporate venture fund.<\\/p><p>The media and education space has been making a steady shift away from traditional print and television to new models of delivery and distribution. Seeing the trend, Sanoma sought to partner and invest in startups that could provide different ways to reach students, distribute information and produce content.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColour\":\"black\"}},\"132\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"5 Converge to Compete in Amsterdam\",\"text\":\"<p>Using our existing networks through our Startupbootcamp programs and dedicated research team we began surveying Europe for startups that could supply innovative shifts in Sanoma\\u2019s business model.<\\/p><p>Our efforts spanned 22 European countries. We evaluated over 500 startups, encouraging over 100 high quality applications. From these, we hand-picked the best 50 to participate in the challenge.<\\/p><p><span><\\/span>The top 5 teams won an all-expenses paid trip to Amsterdam for the competition Final.<\\/p>\",\"image\":[\"123\"],\"align\":\"right\"}},\"133\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"\\\"Our efforts spanned 22 European countries. We evaluated over 500 startups, encouraging over 100 high quality applications. From these, we hand-picked the best 50 to participate in the challenge.\\\"\",\"image\":[\"123\"]}},\"134\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"\",\"text\":\"<p>The two-day competition offered startups the chance to work with mentors, Sanoma executives, Sanoma Learning industry experts and SanomaVenture\\u2019s investment team.<\\/p><p>By exposing startups to these potential partners and customers, we pushed them to evolve their ideas, while demonstrating the potential benefits of collaboration between corporations and startups.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"135\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Value for Both Sides of the Table\",\"text\":\"<p>As a part of the Sanoma Startup Challenge, the startups were given the opportunity to make their final pitch at THENEXTWEB conference in Amsterdam, live on stage in front of Sanoma executives, investors and the full conference crowd.<\\/p><p>Ultimately, a Danish startup, Labster, which offers next generation laboratory simulations, was named the winner, receiving a cash prize of \\u20ac25,000.<\\/p><p><span><\\/span>To date, Sanoma has invested in 18 different ed-tech startups.<\\/p>\",\"image\":[\"124\"],\"align\":\"right\"}}},\"80\":\"\",\"72\":[\"124\"],\"100\":\"Get in touch\",\"99\":\"Ready to talk about what innovation means for you?\",\"67\":\"We were pleasantly surprised by the diversity and the high quality of the startups that applied ... the challenge has already given us interesting new connections for both SanomaVentures, for potential investments, as for Sanoma Learning for future cooperation and partnerships\",\"69\":\"Herman Kienhuis\",\"68\":\"Investment Director\",\"71\":[\"225\"]}}', '2016-11-15 11:15:38', '2016-11-15 11:15:38', '6808c737-f4cb-4cbd-b35f-55e74783814e'),
 ('335', '158', '4', '15', 'en_us', '8', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"15\",\"title\":\"Startup MENA: Empowering Entrepreneurship in the Middle East and North Africa\",\"slug\":\"startup-mena-empowering-entrepreneurs-in-the-middle-east-and-north-africa\",\"postDate\":1477415700,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"70\":[\"156\"],\"91\":\"\",\"47\":{\"159\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"In 2014, we partnered with The Danish Foreign Ministry to deliver a 2 year program stimulating economic growth in the private sectors of Egypt, Jordan and Tunisia. \",\"image\":[\"147\"]}},\"160\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Seeding a Startup Ecosystem\",\"text\":\"<p>Since 2003 The Danish government has been actively collaborating with the Middle East and North Africa to strengthen cooperation and support the ongoing reform and democratization of the region.<\\/p><p>However, political revolution and unemployment still threaten to impede the successful democratization process in some countries in the region. Stimulating job creation has therefore become a key objective for The Danish-Arab Partnership Program across the region.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"161\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Job Creation in the MENA Region\",\"text\":\"<p>In 2014, high rates of unemployment continued, particularly amongst young people, despite many being well-educated, ready to work and keen to actively help shape the future of their countries.<\\/p><p>It was in this context that we were challenged to design and deliver a program with The Danish Foreign Ministry: creating jobs and growth through entrepreneurship.<\\/p>\",\"image\":[\"151\"],\"align\":\"left\"}},\"162\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Leading Through Value \",\"text\":\"<p>As our team was new to the region, we knew that the existing ecosystem would measure us on the basis of the value we displayed. To ensure our event attendees left with new insights, knowledge, and inspiration, we brought in experts, high-profile international mentors, and investors to all our events.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"163\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"We Delivered a Range of Events to Support and Encourage Local Startups:\",\"text\":\"<ul><li>Two investment labs<\\/li><li>Two 48 hour hackathons<\\/li><li>Four women\\u2019s meetups<\\/li><li>Six mini bootcamps<\\/li><li>Three open offices<\\/li><li>Two job fairs<\\/li><li>Two investor pitch events<\\/li><li>One corporate matchmaking event<\\/li><li>A series of intensive, high impact workshops<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"image\":[\"150\"],\"align\":\"right\"}},\"164\":{\"type\":\"imageBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"152\",\"153\",\"154\",\"155\"]}},\"165\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Over Two Years We Hosted 27 Events Across Jordan, Egypt and Tunisia \",\"text\":\"<p>90+ jobs created<br>820+ entrepreneurs<br>70+ partners<br>130+ startups engaged<br>160+ mentors engaged<br>10.000+ in network<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColour\":\"white\"}},\"226\":{\"type\":\"videoBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"youtubeVideoId\":\"9B-fW-MSg5Q\"}}},\"80\":\"\",\"72\":[\"147\"],\"100\":\"Get in touch\",\"99\":\"Take an ecosystem approach for real impact\",\"67\":\"It was an amazing experience \\u2014 the level of knowledge from mentors and investors was beyond any events we have attended.\",\"69\":\"Founder, ZEX\",\"68\":\"Moataz Kotb\",\"71\":[\"230\"]}}', '2016-11-15 11:18:29', '2016-11-15 11:18:29', 'ac9d6606-9045-420e-aede-d1ce9b827699'),
 ('336', '169', '4', '15', 'en_us', '10', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"15\",\"title\":\"Making Copenhagen a Nordic FinTech Hub \",\"slug\":\"study-and-recommendations-for-making-copenhagen-a-nordic-fintech-hub\",\"postDate\":1477421940,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"70\":[\"218\"],\"91\":\"\",\"47\":{\"170\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Mapping an Industry \",\"text\":\"<p>In 2015 we were approached by a group of organizations including Finansforbundet, Danish Bankers Association, City of Copenhagen, DJ\\u00d8F, Nets, Saxo Bank, BEC, Tryg and CFIR for an opportunity to analyze and describe FinTech in Copenhagen.&nbsp;<\\/p><p>The nine partners wanted to map the Danish FinTech environment, to benchmark Copenhagen against other cities and to identify initiatives that should be taken in order to develop and strengthen the FinTech ecosystem in Copenhagen.<\\/p>\",\"image\":[\"167\"],\"align\":\"left\"}},\"171\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"A 360 Degree View \",\"text\":\"<p>Oxford Research and Rainmaking were chosen as consultants for the analysis. While Oxford Research has a deep knowledge of the Danish FinTech cluster from an institutional level; Rainmaking intimately knows the Danish startup scene and the international FinTech environment through our Startupbootcamp FinTech accelerators. Together we were able to partner to provide a holistic overview of the ecosystem, spanning both startup and corporate activity.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"172\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Thorough Investigation\",\"text\":\"<p>We conducted five workshops focusing on different areas: research and education, investors, startups, regulation and public authorities, incubators\\/accelerators and corporates. It was important for the validity of the results that actors who know the FinTech ecosystem and the challenges for FinTech all had the opportunity to contribute, so, we involved over 250 people across all levels of the ecosystem, from executives to developers.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColour\":\"white\"}},\"227\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Download the Summary Report Here\",\"text\":\"<p><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/s3.amazonaws.com\\/rainmaking\\/websiteImages\\/Copenhagen-as-a-Nordic-Fintech-Hub-summary-report.pdf#asset:340\\\">Recommendations for Making Copenhagen a Nordic FinTech Hub<\\/a><\\/p>\",\"image\":[\"228\"],\"align\":\"right\"}},\"174\":{\"type\":\"videoBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"youtubeVideoId\":\"QD7STd0ZP88\"}}},\"80\":\"\",\"72\":[\"175\"],\"100\":\"Get in touch\",\"99\":\"Find out more about this study\",\"67\":\"It was an absolute privilege to take part in a study that could help position a relatively small city as a global hub\",\"69\":\"Partner at Rainmaking\",\"68\":\"Carsten K\\u00f8lbek\",\"71\":[\"229\"]}}', '2016-11-15 11:25:00', '2016-11-15 11:25:00', 'a52a162a-942f-4cf6-a0c9-1aa17c9e9a24'),
 ('337', '2', '1', '15', 'en_us', '30', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Homepage\",\"slug\":\"homepage\",\"postDate\":1476710702,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"75\":[\"18\"],\"4\":\"We created Startupbootcamp \\u2014 the largest industry focused accelerator network in the world with 16 programs across five continents. \",\"76\":[\"20\"],\"6\":\"We have built 25 of our own startups, achieving 5 notable exits and lead over 350 startup investments. \",\"9\":[\"195\",\"69\",\"24\",\"57\"],\"3\":\"Partner with proven entrepreneurs. Harness startup behaviors that complement what you\\u2019re doing already. Discover what else you could be doing.\",\"11\":\"We live in a world that is changing faster than ever.\\u00a0Where past performance is no guarantee of future success. We know from experience\\u00a0that no matter how well you plan\\u00a0new ventures,\\u00a0sometimes they just don\\u2019t work. This is part of our approach to\\u00a0helping our partners discover innovation for\\u00a0their own organizations. If something works \\u2013 or if it doesn\\u2019t \\u2013 you\\u2019ll know about it.   Many claim to have the answers but\\u00a0hide behind powerpoint presentations and buzzwords. We accept that we don\'t have all the answers, but we do know the right questions to ask.\\u00a0  Read the\\u00a0latest thoughts and lessons learned\\u00a0from experts across the Rainmaking community.\\u00a0\",\"89\":\"Nektarios Liolios\",\"90\":[\"287\"],\"78\":[\"56\"],\"88\":[\"292\",\"299\",\"304\",\"293\",\"305\",\"295\",\"298\",\"301\"],\"7\":\"We partner with organizations to deliver training. Engage with startups. Build digital products and launch new ventures.\",\"12\":\"We love results, not presentations. \",\"8\":\"We give you the mindset, skills and confidence to ideate, create and scale new business.   Collaboratively and confidently. No buzzwords. Just plain English.  \\r\\nAnd we\\u2019ll make sure it happens. We love results not presentations. Actions not words. \\r\\n\\r\\nJust see for yourself.\",\"77\":[\"19\"],\"5\":\"We created Rainmaking Loft coworking spaces. Serving over 1,000 entrepreneurs in London, Berlin and Copenhagen.\"}}', '2016-11-15 11:30:47', '2016-11-15 11:30:47', 'bb7f4f7c-50e8-40e8-872a-9583a2fb0b8d'),
 ('338', '2', '1', '15', 'en_us', '31', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Homepage\",\"slug\":\"homepage\",\"postDate\":1476710702,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"75\":[\"18\"],\"4\":\"We created Startupbootcamp \\u2014 the largest industry focused accelerator network in the world with 16 programs across five continents. \",\"76\":[\"20\"],\"6\":\"We have built 25 of our own startups, achieving 5 notable exits and lead over 350 startup investments. \",\"9\":[\"195\",\"69\",\"24\",\"57\"],\"3\":\"Partner with proven entrepreneurs. Harness startup behaviors that complement what you\\u2019re doing already. And discover what else you could be doing.\",\"11\":\"We live in a world that is changing faster than ever.\\u00a0Where past performance is no guarantee of future success. We know from experience\\u00a0that no matter how well you plan\\u00a0new ventures,\\u00a0sometimes they just don\\u2019t work. This is part of our approach to\\u00a0helping our partners discover innovation for\\u00a0their own organizations. If something works \\u2013 or if it doesn\\u2019t \\u2013 you\\u2019ll know about it.   Many claim to have the answers but\\u00a0hide behind powerpoint presentations and buzzwords. We accept that we don\'t have all the answers, but we do know the right questions to ask.\\u00a0  Read the\\u00a0latest thoughts and lessons learned\\u00a0from experts across the Rainmaking community.\\u00a0\",\"89\":\"Nektarios Liolios\",\"90\":[\"287\"],\"78\":[\"56\"],\"88\":[\"292\",\"299\",\"304\",\"293\",\"305\",\"295\",\"298\",\"301\"],\"7\":\"We partner with organizations to deliver training. Engage with startups. Build digital products and launch new ventures.\",\"12\":\"We love results, not presentations. \",\"8\":\"We give you the mindset, skills and confidence to ideate, create and scale new business.   Collaboratively and confidently. No buzzwords. Just plain English.  \\r\\nAnd we\\u2019ll make sure it happens. We love results not presentations. Actions not words. \\r\\n\\r\\nJust see for yourself.\",\"77\":[\"19\"],\"5\":\"We created Rainmaking Loft coworking spaces. Serving over 1,000 entrepreneurs in London, Berlin and Copenhagen.\"}}', '2016-11-15 11:32:31', '2016-11-15 11:32:31', 'fa524201-1cfe-4175-83fd-0b5691820736'),
 ('339', '195', '4', '15', 'en_us', '9', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"15\",\"title\":\"New Ways of Working for Lloyd\'s Banking Group \",\"slug\":\"how-lloyds-banking-group-stays-ahead-of-fintech-evolution\",\"postDate\":1477478580,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"70\":[\"178\"],\"91\":\"\",\"47\":{\"196\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Partnering With Market Leaders\",\"text\":\"<p>Since 2014 we have been helping to shape the global evolution of FinTech. Together with market leaders like MasterCard, Lloyds Banking Group, Santander, Thomson Reuters, PWC and Rabobank we run Startupbootcamp accelerator programs, design corporate innovation programs, and establish commercial connections between startups and established players.<\\/p>\",\"image\":[\"180\"],\"align\":\"left\"}},\"198\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"Each year we scout upwards of 3000 FinTech startups from across the globe. With accelerator programs in Singapore, London and New York, and 50+ FinTech events across almost every continent. \",\"image\":[\"179\"]}},\"199\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Early Access to Innovation\",\"text\":\"<p>We select less than 1% of these startups for a Startupbootcamp cohort. This ensures our partners are collaborating with the best talent, often generating pilots, commercial partnerships and co-created solutions. Meanwhile, through the selection process itself, partners are exposed to evolving technology and business model trends at an early stage.<\\/p>\",\"image\":[\"181\"],\"align\":\"right\"}},\"200\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Staying in Front of the Curve with Lloyd\'s \",\"text\":\"<p>Lloyds Banking Group has been a partner on our Startupbootcamp FinTech program since 2014. The partnership came at a time when the bank was undertaking a large-scale digital transformation program, and presented an ideal platform to test new ideas and connect with the wider FinTech ecosystem.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColour\":\"black\"}},\"201\":{\"type\":\"textBlockWithImages\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"\",\"text\":\"<p>Lloyds\\u2019 goal is to scan the market for innovation and find new opportunities to provide better service to their customers. The relationship is beneficial for both parties: the FinTech startup has access to subject matter experts, launching customers and scarce assets like data sets. For Lloyds it is beneficial because they are able to learn about new technology, business models, see the results within the market and deduce important lessons to stay ahead and deliver value to their customers.<\\/p>\",\"image\":[\"182\"],\"align\":\"left\"}},\"202\":{\"type\":\"quoteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"The relationship with Startupbootcamp has been the first step towards collaborating with startups and to support our digital transformation agenda. By working with innovative partners we are able to deliver even better customer propositions and services.\",\"quoteName\":\"Claire Calmejane\",\"role\":\"Head of Innovation\",\"image\":[\"189\"]}},\"203\":{\"type\":\"soundbyteBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"Collaborating with Startupbootcamp alumni WoraPay \\u2013 is said to have saved Lloyds Banking Group employees 10,000 days of work. \",\"image\":[\"185\"]}},\"204\":{\"type\":\"textBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"New Ways of Working\",\"text\":\"<p>For Lloyds, collaborating with the FinTech sector also provides inspiring examples of agility and working practices that refresh Lloyd\\u2019s thinking and approach to delivering digital services. <\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The partnership gave Lloyds the chance to be involved in dedicated events such as FinTech Lounges and hackathons, presenting another opportunity to experience new ways of working.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColour\":\"grey\"}},\"205\":{\"type\":\"imageBlock\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"191\",\"193\",\"194\"]}}},\"80\":\"1\",\"72\":[\"179\"],\"100\":\"Get in touch\",\"99\":\"Need more entreprenurial thinking in your business?\",\"67\":\"Our relationship with Rainmaking has given hundreds of our colleagues access to new tools and new ways of working that they are using to become inspiring intrapreneurs and to develop new propositions and services for our customers\\r\\n\",\"69\":\"Director of Innovation\",\"68\":\"Claire Calmejane\",\"71\":[\"189\"]}}', '2016-11-15 12:20:00', '2016-11-15 12:20:00', 'bf27da39-14d6-4dd6-8602-1aa6c7d055f1'),
