 ('9', '42', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'We partnered with Danske Bank to create TheHub.dk, a platform that aims to relieve the pains of Danish startups and provide a platform for Danske Bank to engage with the startup ecosystem. ', NULL, '2016-10-24 18:58:23', '2016-11-15 16:30:05', '73aeb3de-fbc3-4663-9cea-df4a625c2fdb'),
 ('10', '43', 'en_us', 'Participating in the Future ', '<p>Danske Bank came to us in the Fall of 2015 with an exciting challenge: to create and run a project that would add value to Danish startups and accelerate the growth of early stage companies. </p>\n\n<p>Danske Bank wanted to test new forms of engagement with emerging businesses. By actively participating in the Danish startup ecosystem, they gain early insights into new technologies and business models that could impact their business in the future.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>By supporting startups at an early stage, helping them succeed and grow, Danske Bank also creates a wider stream of potential future customers.</p>', 'grey', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-24 18:58:23', '2016-11-15 16:30:05', '479f9f5e-f69d-4769-938c-4bf7858a1216'),
 ('11', '44', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'An Online Recruiting Platform, Community and Resource Center ', '<p>After over 100 founder interviews, we found three major pain points faced by Danish startups:</p>\n\n<ol><li>Recruitment: lack of a nationwide, startup focused job board</li><li>Funding: navigating the overwhelming number of investors and funding options to find the right choice</li><li>Knowledge Sharing: capitalizing on the experience of successful founders to accelerate progress</li></ol><p>With these three problems in mind, we created The Hub.</p>', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-24 18:58:23', '2016-11-15 16:30:05', '143e53e4-220d-46c2-aed7-5839f0cdeaa8'),
 ('13', '46', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '\"We received far more applications through the Hub compared to elsewhere. All the applicants were relevant and part of our target group. For those reasons, I would recommend the Hub (and have already done it)\"', 'Happy Hub User', '', NULL, NULL, '2016-10-24 18:58:23', '2016-11-15 16:30:05', '7d972261-fdef-4e06-a241-9b193e67347a'),
 ('14', '47', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Connection With Investors ', '<p>To help navigate the funding options available to Danish startups, our next solution was to create a tool which could match startups with the most relevant options for them, based on their industry, experience, level of maturity and team size. This included profiles of the top 50 investors in Denmark.</p>', 'right', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-24 18:58:23', '2016-11-15 16:30:05', '8fea76b9-540b-456b-9d7c-6abdfc9e7933'),
 ('15', '48', 'en_us', 'Access to Expert Knowledge', '<p>Knowledge sharing posed the greatest challenge. The majority of the information startups need is topical, specific to their industry, stage and product.</p>\n\n<p>The Hub therefore needed to address the need for both startup specific, and generic content. To achieve this, we’ve started to develop a mentor matching scheme to pair startups with relevant advisors.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Meanwhile, we’ve also developed a number of tools to share best practices around some of the steps almost all startups follow. From raising funds to gaining the very first customers.</p>', 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-24 18:58:23', '2016-11-15 16:30:05', 'cb81e7f2-e02f-4e41-9712-1bcb22d3cf53'),
 ('16', '49', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Widening The Hub’s Reach', '<p>Today, the Hub is the largest startup recruitment site in Denmark. And, we’re now applying what we’ve learned across the Nordics, launching Hubs in Norway and Sweden, opening up opportunities for cross-country applications in markets where Danske Bank is most active.</p>', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-24 18:58:23', '2016-11-15 16:30:05', 'f0b7a231-b6b9-4514-8e66-ed7bdbed19c7'),
 ('17', '58', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Finding the Driving Edge of Startup Talent', '<p>Daimler, a partner of Startupbootcamp Smart Transportation, owner of Mercedes Benz and the largest commercial vehicle manufacturer in the world, came to us looking for startups that could help them gain an edge against competition and stay up to date on emerging technology.</p>\n\n<p>We sourced over 1,000 startups from across 18 countries and identified a number of forces that are shaping the future of transportation and mobility.</p>', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 11:04:54', '2016-11-15 18:13:10', '3702d8ac-240c-4426-9a21-7c972f3617e8'),
 ('18', '59', 'en_us', 'Staying In the Fast Lane', '<p>As cars have become connected, electric and autonomous, Daimler has recognized that they must identify new innovations early in order to stay at the forefront of current technological advancements.</p>\n\n<p>Our challenge was to find the next generation of startups that could help Daimler overtake their competition.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With this in mind, Daimler asked us to source startup talent, and identify trends that are driving innovation within the smart mobility space.</p>', 'grey', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 11:04:54', '2016-11-15 18:13:10', '9ee23aed-5672-4b04-9ddc-08d1a4c77cc2'),
 ('19', '60', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, '¡Hola Brazil!', '<p>Our sourcing team screened startups from around the globe. And, identified the most interesting startups for Daimler.</p>\n\n<p>Beginning with a world wide scope, we quickly identified Europe and Brazil as exciting areas for new talent.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Responding to global trends, we saw that Brazil’s growth had opened up new markets and created untapped opportunities for startups. In particular, urbanization and rapid population growth present problems that startups are actively finding innovative solutions to. This led us to a new hotbed of talent that was generally underrepresented in mainstream sources.</p>', 'right', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 11:04:54', '2016-11-15 18:13:10', '4b01438c-4db8-4e02-9cb3-293a136b9495'),
 ('20', '61', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '\"Beginning with a world wide scope, we quickly identified Europe and Brazil as exciting areas for new talent.\"', NULL, '2016-10-25 11:04:54', '2016-11-15 18:13:10', '5f818e90-88a9-4f1e-b7c7-665970e079e2'),
 ('21', '62', 'en_us', 'Getting the Whole Picture', '<p>At the end of the two month sourcing period we had:</p>\n\n<ul><li>Sourced startups from 87 data sources</li><li>Covered 18 countries</li><li>Reviewed 1759 startups</li><li>Selected 326 startups for further review</li></ul>', 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 11:04:54', '2016-11-15 18:13:10', '56393a6a-ae5c-46e9-8a62-0dc43d95d1b9'),
 ('22', '63', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Delivering Startups, Trends, and Actionable Intel', '<p>Our internal panel reviewed and assessed these startups, refining the selection to a top 40. These were presented back to Daimler alongside a trend report capturing industry insights, further highlighting opportunities for engagement within the startup world.</p>\n\n<p>Today Daimler remains actively involved in the startup ecosystem, as a partner in our Smart Transportation &amp; Energy Startupbootcamp and continues to pursue new innovations.</p>', 'right', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 11:04:54', '2016-11-15 18:13:10', '7b7464ce-25af-4b6b-9d02-0ccf7249caae'),
 ('24', '71', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '\"we were approached by Castrol innoVentures to help increase its deal flow and strengthen its presence and visibility in the global startup community.\"', NULL, '2016-10-25 11:30:32', '2016-11-15 16:29:52', 'fc2454cd-0c76-4db1-b25c-468e07feae2c'),
 ('25', '72', 'en_us', 'How to Put Castrol On the Global Startup Map', '<p>In today’s venture capital environment, startups are not short on sources of investment. There are hundreds of institutional firms, angel investors and CVC’s.</p>\n\n<p>We needed a way to put Castrol on startups’ radar as a valuable partner, both to work with, and to have on their cap table.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The focus was for us to find startups innovating in 4 strategic areas: Smart Mobility, next generation engineering, intelligent operations, and responsible Castrol.</p>', 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 11:30:32', '2016-11-15 16:29:52', '704c39be-2d0f-4079-ae6a-c739804b92cc'),
 ('26', '74', 'en_us', 'Going Beyond Motor Oil', '<p>In 2012, we were approached by Castrol innoVentures to help increase its deal flow and strengthen its presence and visibility in the global startup community. </p>\n\n<p>At the time, Castrol had just set up its strategic innovation and investment arm in order to bring additional value to its existing business areas, and to take Castrol beyond motor oils and lubricants and into future focused revenue streams.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Together with the team at Castrol innoVentures, we designed a global pitch competition to act as a sourcing and screening program, allowing us to meet and evaluate startups relevant for Castrol to work with.The program resulted in Castrol making a direct investment in one startup and commercial partnerships with seven others.</p>', 'grey', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 12:37:34', '2016-11-15 16:29:52', 'b6d5d59b-a4b2-4d0c-a75c-efb14751c1de'),
 ('27', '75', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Building a Startup Friendly Brand', '<p>We built a brand around the project: the Castrol 20/20 Challenge.</p>\n\n<p>A selection of startup finalists would receive free flights and accommodation to London or Shanghai in order to pitch their business to Venture Capitalists and Castrol executives. The winning team was to receive 10,000 USD.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A brand website was launched, promoting the competition to potential applicants and spreading the word throughout the global startup community. Both the brand and website were fundamental in positioning Castrol as a company ready to make investments and meaningfully engage with startups.</p>', 'right', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 12:37:34', '2016-11-15 16:29:52', 'e804876b-cc6a-4994-aaf8-044de6d0f156'),
 ('28', '76', 'en_us', 'Over 2,000 Startups Reviewed', '<p>With our marketing efforts driving competition applications, and outreach from our dedicated sourcing team, we attracted and reviewed over 2,000 startups.</p>\n\n<p>Drawing on our experience mentoring and selecting startups for our Startupbootcamp programs and our own investments, we created a shortlist of 20 companies based on their applications and 1-1 interviews.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Together with Castrol innoVentures, we conducted further interviews to narrow the selection to just five startups in each of two competition finals in London and Shanghai.</p>', 'grey', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 12:37:34', '2016-11-15 16:29:52', '3748e3c0-1c0b-46cb-a1f8-717d524f75c2'),
 ('29', '77', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Preparing Startups for Collaboration with Corporates', '<p>In both London and Shanghai, we worked with the startups and mentors one day prior to the final events to prepare the teams. We helped them hone their pitches and introduced ways that they could more effectively work with major corporations.T</p>\n\n<p>he following day, the startups pitched and met with over 30 Venture Capitalists, alongside executives from Castrol and other notable corporations like 3M.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The events not only provided immense value to the startups, in terms of connections and networking with experts, but also gave Castrol a platform to engage with the startups early on.</p>', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 12:37:34', '2016-11-15 16:29:52', 'daa10ac2-a0e1-4343-b763-940b243d47c1'),
 ('30', '78', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '\"Castrol 2020 Challenge provided impressive and innovative ideas and we work with 7 out of 10 teams from the 2012 program\"', 'Roy Williamson', 'Castrol InnoVentures, Managing Director', NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 12:37:34', '2016-11-15 16:29:52', '0cdad9c7-67ec-4c87-823c-f01b2d35b696'),
 ('31', '82', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 12:42:54', '2016-11-15 16:29:52', '60fd1c83-aafc-4c08-86d2-425c7119e530'),
 ('32', '83', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Creating and Capitalising on Investment Opportunities', '<p>Castrol InnoVentures ultimately invested in Greensteam, a ground breaking technology company specialising in energy saving solutions for commercial vessels.</p>\n\n<p>The events proved to be a success, so we hosted a second edition, this time exclusively in Shanghai.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To this day, Castrol innoVentures remains an active player in the mobility space and has made further investments in a range of startups.</p>', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 12:42:54', '2016-11-15 16:29:52', 'f0d5411c-ca45-4153-adb0-5c768868c2a6'),
 ('33', '87', 'en_us', 'Collaboration Between SME\'s, Startups, and Corporates', '<p>Following the success of our ecosystem development work in the MENA regions, we were trusted to co-create the 2015 EU-GCC program. A pilot initiative intended to promote trade between the EU and GCC as well as increase cooperation between corporates, SME’s and startups.</p><p>We partnered with The Danish Confederation of Industry, Business Europe, and the Federation of Gulf Cooperation Council Chambers (‘GCC’) to design and deliver this project, funded by the EU Commission.</p>', 'grey', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 13:00:39', '2016-11-15 10:51:08', '35bb2c8e-249c-4e65-9fed-52d96ce7b1b9'),
 ('34', '88', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Optimizing Relations', '<p>Despite a past characterized by sociopolitical challenges, the GCC and EU are increasingly reliant on each other for trade and investment. The GCC stands as the fifth top trading partner with the EU and accounts for over €100 Billion in EU goods exports.</p><p>While trade is increasing steadily year over year, the majority is still based on mineral fuels and industrial products.</p>', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 13:00:39', '2016-11-15 10:51:08', '4518c8df-3b60-4999-ac73-a3d28ffa130c'),
 ('35', '89', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Our challenge was to promote trade bilaterally in underrepresented areas such as services and technology, while also increasing collaboration in the development of new innovations.', NULL, '2016-10-25 13:00:39', '2016-11-15 10:51:08', 'ad8da98b-711f-4c75-aca6-57aebcf0e0ee'),
 ('36', '90', 'en_us', 'Top Tech Talent', '<p>Targeting recruitment first, we built a job board tailored specifically to startups.</p>\n\n<p>We found that startups rely on their own networks and traditional job boards for hiring. But they were missing something fit for purpose. Specifically for entrepreneurs. Targeting job seekers interested in joining startups.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We’ve now created over 550 startup profiles and see over 11000 weekly visits, converting to 600 weekly applications. This is paired with great feedback from both startups and applicants using the site.</p>', 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 13:04:48', '2016-11-15 16:30:05', '3f12336a-1cbf-4598-9d96-cc96d7ae3326'),
 ('37', '95', 'en_us', 'Building on Existing Platforms', '<p>Having already built up a strong local presence in the GCC region and Europe, and proven the success of our workshop format through our Startup MENA Program, we were able to draw on our existing network of engaged corporates and ecosystem players to design a series of premium workshops and match-making events.</p>', 'white', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 13:38:10', '2016-11-15 10:51:08', '3b3f3391-bf01-4f31-9397-1c364f6bbc0c'),
 ('38', '96', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, '24 Events in 10 Countries ', '<p>Over the course of 2015 we ran 24 events across 10 countries. And, successfully highlighted disruptive startups from the GCC, training entrepreneurs, matching corporates to startups for commercial partnerships, and promoting the Gulf as a market to EU startups and SMEs.</p>', 'right', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 13:38:10', '2016-11-15 10:51:08', '770de257-ecfb-48aa-9f42-d9bef4e61479'),
 ('39', '97', 'en_us', 'We Designed and Delivered:', '<ul><li>Intensive workshops in Kuwait City, Doha, Muscat, Dubai, Manama, Jeddah, London, Berlin, Brussels and Rome</li><li>Match-making events in London and Dubai</li><li>An international pitch challenge touring Kuwait, Bahrain, UAE, Qatar, Saudi Arabia and Oman</li><li>An online matchmaking portal: EU-GCC Connect</li></ul>', 'grey', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 13:38:10', '2016-11-15 10:51:08', 'e03556d2-9aea-4369-9747-938d367473f3'),
 ('40', '98', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 13:38:10', '2016-11-15 10:51:08', '8b15b060-2c36-4045-bb6e-fa6f07295b7e'),
 ('41', '99', 'en_us', 'Continued Operation', '<p>Building on the success of the EU-GCC program in 2015, the initiative will continue to run until 2018.</p><p>The data and reports generated by Rainmaking will be used as the bedrock of further efforts to increase trade and investment across various industries.</p><p>The Danish Confederation of Industry, Business Europe, and the Federation of Gulf Cooperation Council Chambers are all driven to to progress further; forging closer links, removing regulatory barriers, and increasing trade.</p>', 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 13:38:10', '2016-11-15 10:51:08', '6c6bd381-1730-4052-8d2d-e2ae2d096edf'),
 ('42', '109', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'A three day hackathon followed by an intensive five day program, transforming ideas into viable businesses.', NULL, '2016-10-25 14:43:45', '2016-11-15 16:28:54', '15cdede5-5685-4359-b90b-6816a4044827'),
 ('43', '110', 'en_us', 'Responding To Changing Times', '<p>Majid Al Futtaim runs Malls and Carrefour hypermarkets across the Middle East, North Africa and Central Asia including the Mall of the Emirates, famous for its indoor ski slope. </p>\n\n<p>Their large physical footprint has given them a distinctive advantage in the retail market, however, with consumer behaviors evolving towards an increasingly digital experience, Majid Al Futtaim wanted to explore how they could be more innovative; both in their customer experiences, and their ways of working.</p>', 'grey', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 14:43:45', '2016-11-15 16:28:54', '515be4cd-3dd7-49e9-859e-f61523f87988'),
 ('44', '111', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, '48 Hours to Create a New Experience for Dubai', '<p>As the first phase of the “Next Great Moment” challenge, we created a two day hackathon. This inspired Majid Al Futtaim’s employees to refine internal ideas for new and innovative products and services in just 48 hours.</p>\n\n<p>In addition to generating new and innovative ideas, the event gave employees direct experience applying a more entrepreneurial mindset. It also served to create both internal and external excitement around Majid Al Futtaim\'s innovative approach.</p>', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 14:43:45', '2016-11-15 16:28:54', 'cce65400-3371-407d-87e5-ae3f9edeba37'),
 ('45', '112', 'en_us', '', '<p>From over 1300 applications, 83 talented individuals were selected to attend this intensive experience. By bringing together employees from across the company, we reinforced the importance of collaboration to drive innovation and escape the natural silos of the organization.</p>', 'grey', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 14:43:45', '2016-11-15 16:28:55', 'c0960277-c55d-4e30-8e1f-ef6f62440550'),
 ('46', '113', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Thinking Big', '<p>Each attendee had just 60 seconds to pitch their idea, before teams formed around the 10 most popular concepts.</p>\n\n<p>They then had just two days to test and evolve their value proposition through customer interviews, and industry research. Finally, they distilled their updated business idea into a 3 minute pitch.</p>\n\n<p>Throughout the weekend, teams were exposed to new methodologies; an intensive series of exercises and workshops which encouraged attendees to “Think Big”, introducing them to Global Trends to further inspire their efforts.</p>', 'right', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 14:43:45', '2016-11-15 16:28:55', '4d1a18e6-ca30-44d1-ab79-091289101ef2'),
 ('47', '114', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '\"From over 1300 applications, 83 talented individuals were selected to attend this intensive experience.\"', NULL, '2016-10-25 14:43:45', '2016-11-15 16:28:55', '90bff17a-4986-4b6e-99e5-0314f98bafc7'),
 ('48', '115', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Making the Most of Every Minute', '<p>We held networking events and icebreakers to encourage teams to utilize the event to meet as many colleagues and industry experts as possible.</p>\n\n<p>Expert pitch trainers taught the teams to present with impact, polishing their pitches, and honing presentation skills.</p>\n\n<p>Meanwhile, serial entrepreneurs and thought leaders were on hand to offer the teams mentoring and further training, inspiring participants with startup approaches to propel them forward.</p>', 'right', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 14:43:45', '2016-11-15 16:28:55', '10a01fab-a672-4440-8332-0cb95dad669d'),
 ('49', '116', 'en_us', 'Ideas to Move You: From Dubai to London', '<p>In this supportive, yet challenging, environment, ideas evolved rapidly. <br />A wide range of concepts were developed throughout this process; offering MAF a choice of radically innovative solutions, alongside those which could be quickly implemented.</p>\n\n<p>Two of the most exciting ideas won the prize of 5 weeks in London with Rainmaking. Here, we created an immersive Pop-Up Lab which pushed their business models, teamwork and delivery even further.</p>', 'grey', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 14:43:45', '2016-11-15 16:28:55', 'c3889c33-21bf-4976-b49e-ef669d1ed1cd'),
 ('50', '117', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '\"Two of the most exciting ideas won the prize of 5 weeks in London with Rainmaking.\"', NULL, '2016-10-25 14:43:45', '2016-11-15 16:28:55', '6332597d-f5b5-499b-9b12-341184b7023d'),
 ('51', '118', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'New Skills and New Business', '<p>These teams left the Pop-Up Lab with a new appreciation of Lean Startup approaches, experience conducting customer interviews, and greater insight into working collaboratively in a newly formed team. Equipped with new ways of approaching problems and understanding customer needs they are more able to create meaningful change to MAF\'s business.</p>', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 14:43:45', '2016-11-15 16:28:55', '2f6b3000-90a7-49f0-b0f8-fd0c26b4bfbe'),
 ('53', '120', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'We’ve now created over 550 startup profiles and see over 11000 weekly visits, converting to 600 weekly applications.', NULL, '2016-10-25 15:00:45', '2016-11-15 16:30:05', '8e3f7031-e100-4790-8df2-469b71094803'),
 ('55', '130', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Strategic Deal Flow: A Win-Win', '<p>For this project we were entrusted with finding hopeful EdTech startups with the potential to grow their business together with Sanoma, the Nordic region’s leading media and learning company.</p>\n\n<p>Promising startups were invited to participate in the “Sanoma Startup Challenge - the future of learning,” an event which we designed and delivered to discover promising startup talent.</p>', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 16:21:46', '2016-11-15 16:29:09', '107caccf-906e-47c0-8528-a6d1e64dc8c3'),
 ('56', '131', 'en_us', 'The Future of Learning', '<p>Sanoma Ventures came to us looking for ways to find high quality deal flow for their newly formed corporate venture fund.</p>\n\n<p>The media and education space has been making a steady shift away from traditional print and television to new models of delivery and distribution. Seeing the trend, Sanoma sought to partner and invest in startups that could provide different ways to reach students, distribute information and produce content.</p>', 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 16:21:46', '2016-11-15 16:29:09', '5cf5ec1f-53e1-437b-be29-ab6389362383'),
 ('57', '132', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, '5 Converge to Compete in Amsterdam', '<p>Using our existing networks through our Startupbootcamp programs and dedicated research team we began surveying Europe for startups that could supply innovative shifts in Sanoma’s business model.</p>\n\n<p>Our efforts spanned 22 European countries. We evaluated over 500 startups, encouraging over 100 high quality applications. From these, we hand-picked the best 50 to participate in the challenge.</p>\n\n<p>The top 5 teams won an all-expenses paid trip to Amsterdam for the competition Final.</p>', 'right', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 16:21:46', '2016-11-15 16:29:09', 'd4ec66b5-8e61-4ea8-9f73-4e0065e3f080'),
 ('58', '133', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '\"Our efforts spanned 22 European countries. We evaluated over 500 startups, encouraging over 100 high quality applications. From these, we hand-picked the best 50 to participate in the challenge.\"', NULL, '2016-10-25 16:21:46', '2016-11-15 16:29:09', 'acd1393a-883e-408f-9bb7-3299e4cfec9e'),
 ('59', '134', 'en_us', '', '<p>The two-day competition offered startups the chance to work with mentors, Sanoma executives, Sanoma Learning industry experts and SanomaVenture’s investment team.</p>\n\n<p>By exposing startups to these potential partners and customers, we pushed them to evolve their ideas, while demonstrating the potential benefits of collaboration between corporations and startups.</p>', 'grey', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 16:21:46', '2016-11-15 16:29:09', 'e100ccdf-18f2-47db-ae2a-a118ef4bf44e'),
 ('60', '135', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Value for Both Sides of the Table', '<p>As a part of the Sanoma Startup Challenge, the startups were given the opportunity to make their final pitch at THENEXTWEB conference in Amsterdam, live on stage in front of Sanoma executives, investors and the full conference crowd.</p>\n\n<p>Ultimately, a Danish startup, Labster, which offers next generation laboratory simulations, was named the winner, receiving a cash prize of €25,000.</p>\n\n<p>To date, Sanoma has invested in 18 different ed-tech startups.</p>', 'right', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 16:21:46', '2016-11-15 16:29:09', '54597b9c-3db2-4ce5-913f-fd02a0fa8740'),
 ('61', '159', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'In 2014, we partnered with The Danish Foreign Ministry to deliver a 2 year program stimulating economic growth in the private sectors of Egypt, Jordan and Tunisia. ', NULL, '2016-10-25 17:20:39', '2016-11-15 16:29:26', '157bebf7-e8c8-4182-9318-53c40c9ef33d'),
 ('62', '160', 'en_us', 'Seeding a Startup Ecosystem', '<p>Since 2003 The Danish government has been actively collaborating with the Middle East and North Africa to strengthen cooperation and support the ongoing reform and democratization of the region.</p>\n\n<p>However, political revolution and unemployment still threaten to impede the successful democratization process in some countries in the region. Stimulating job creation has therefore become a key objective for The Danish-Arab Partnership Program across the region.</p>', 'grey', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 17:20:39', '2016-11-15 16:29:26', '0b2ffd52-11af-4ad9-beeb-e89309d52c17'),
 ('63', '161', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Job Creation in the MENA Region', '<p>In 2014, high rates of unemployment continued, particularly amongst young people, despite many being well-educated, ready to work and keen to actively help shape the future of their countries.</p>\n\n<p>It was in this context that we were challenged to design and deliver a program with The Danish Foreign Ministry: creating jobs and growth through entrepreneurship.</p>', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 17:20:39', '2016-11-15 16:29:26', '777614fc-e287-4efd-8a96-76fe5a84a825'),
 ('64', '162', 'en_us', 'Leading Through Value ', '<p>As our team was new to the region, we knew that the existing ecosystem would measure us on the basis of the value we displayed. To ensure our event attendees left with new insights, knowledge, and inspiration, we brought in experts, high-profile international mentors, and investors to all our events.</p>', 'grey', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 17:20:40', '2016-11-15 16:29:27', '27512d03-177a-433e-9a96-3ed9b6dd11df'),
 ('65', '163', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'We Delivered a Range of Events to Support and Encourage Local Startups:', '<ul><li>Two investment labs</li><li>Two 48 hour hackathons</li><li>Four women’s meetups</li><li>Six mini bootcamps</li><li>Three open offices</li><li>Two job fairs</li><li>Two investor pitch events</li><li>One corporate matchmaking event</li><li>A series of intensive, high impact workshops</li></ul>', 'right', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 17:20:40', '2016-11-15 16:29:27', '291a7850-8e8a-4dac-83f8-c0595181ec88'),
 ('66', '164', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 17:20:40', '2016-11-15 16:29:27', '5d0a2a9e-c34e-4cf6-a782-4c8a101e0379'),
 ('67', '165', 'en_us', 'Over Two Years We Hosted 27 Events Across Jordan, Egypt and Tunisia ', '<p>90+ jobs created<br />820+ entrepreneurs<br />70+ partners<br />130+ startups engaged<br />160+ mentors engaged<br />10.000+ in network</p>', 'white', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 17:20:40', '2016-11-15 16:29:27', '848931ad-ae33-4d85-86fe-edb494d160f5'),
 ('68', '166', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'V3RTOLI33Q0', '2016-10-25 18:03:05', '2016-11-15 16:30:05', 'd14ae495-7484-47fd-9293-b9f987e7563e'),
 ('69', '170', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Mapping an Industry ', '<p>In 2015 we were approached by a group of organizations including Finansforbundet, Danish Bankers Association, City of Copenhagen, DJØF, Nets, Saxo Bank, BEC, Tryg and CFIR for an opportunity to analyze and describe FinTech in Copenhagen. </p><p>The nine partners wanted to map the Danish FinTech environment, to benchmark Copenhagen against other cities and to identify initiatives that should be taken in order to develop and strengthen the FinTech ecosystem in Copenhagen.</p>', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 18:59:52', '2016-11-15 11:25:00', '9eb3700e-b081-49de-8356-e5db1f4cdb95'),
 ('70', '171', 'en_us', 'A 360 Degree View ', '<p>Oxford Research and Rainmaking were chosen as consultants for the analysis. While Oxford Research has a deep knowledge of the Danish FinTech cluster from an institutional level; Rainmaking intimately knows the Danish startup scene and the international FinTech environment through our Startupbootcamp FinTech accelerators. Together we were able to partner to provide a holistic overview of the ecosystem, spanning both startup and corporate activity.</p>', 'grey', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 18:59:52', '2016-11-15 11:25:00', '5bd03103-ae59-4b2d-aa43-3f1e7ee8e7c3'),
 ('71', '172', 'en_us', 'Thorough Investigation', '<p>We conducted five workshops focusing on different areas: research and education, investors, startups, regulation and public authorities, incubators/accelerators and corporates. It was important for the validity of the results that actors who know the FinTech ecosystem and the challenges for FinTech all had the opportunity to contribute, so, we involved over 250 people across all levels of the ecosystem, from executives to developers.</p>', 'white', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-25 18:59:52', '2016-11-15 11:25:00', '83da3b62-85b5-416b-b495-2494315c4f89'),
 ('73', '174', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'QD7STd0ZP88', '2016-10-25 18:59:52', '2016-11-15 11:25:00', 'df9b226e-7bb2-472a-afb9-91e2877af7f7'),
 ('74', '176', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'yEzjhZOcJAg', '2016-10-25 19:10:09', '2016-11-15 16:28:55', '1b964af6-c36b-4ca5-beff-aa67b0ba6691'),
 ('76', '196', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Partnering With Market Leaders', '<p>Since 2014 we have been helping to shape the global evolution of FinTech. Together with market leaders like MasterCard, Lloyds Banking Group, Santander, Thomson Reuters, PWC and Rabobank we run Startupbootcamp accelerator programs, design corporate innovation programs, and establish commercial connections between startups and established players.</p>', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-26 10:43:50', '2016-11-15 16:28:02', 'baa61176-59af-41b4-a016-07ec72e4b0d7'),
 ('78', '198', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Each year we scout upwards of 3000 FinTech startups from across the globe. With accelerator programs in Singapore, London and New York, and 50+ FinTech events across almost every continent. ', NULL, '2016-10-26 10:43:50', '2016-11-15 16:28:02', 'f4683053-a38d-4c84-9fda-7605b21e557f'),
 ('79', '199', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Early Access to Innovation', '<p>We select less than 1% of these startups for a Startupbootcamp cohort. This ensures our partners are collaborating with the best talent, often generating pilots, commercial partnerships and co-created solutions. Meanwhile, through the selection process itself, partners are exposed to evolving technology and business model trends at an early stage.</p>', 'right', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-26 10:43:50', '2016-11-15 16:28:03', 'd3854d88-e8a4-439f-8694-210c3214d441'),
 ('80', '200', 'en_us', 'Staying in Front of the Curve with Lloyd\'s ', '<p>Lloyds Banking Group has been a partner on our Startupbootcamp FinTech program since 2014. The partnership came at a time when the bank was undertaking a large-scale digital transformation program, and presented an ideal platform to test new ideas and connect with the wider FinTech ecosystem.</p>', 'black', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-26 10:43:50', '2016-11-15 16:28:03', 'c6d3d995-64a1-44a4-aa4d-dffcb132f57c'),
 ('81', '201', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<p>Lloyds’ goal is to scan the market for innovation and find new opportunities to provide better service to their customers. The relationship is beneficial for both parties: the FinTech startup has access to subject matter experts, launching customers and scarce assets like data sets. For Lloyds it is beneficial because they are able to learn about new technology, business models, see the results within the market and deduce important lessons to stay ahead and deliver value to their customers.</p>', 'left', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-26 10:43:50', '2016-11-15 16:28:03', '3968cfce-b01a-453b-8f58-e0e744d30c84'),
 ('82', '202', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The relationship with Startupbootcamp has been the first step towards collaborating with startups and to support our digital transformation agenda. By working with innovative partners we are able to deliver even better customer propositions and services.', 'Claire Calmejane', 'Head of Innovation', NULL, NULL, '2016-10-26 10:43:50', '2016-11-15 16:28:03', '947c6cec-bcbc-4915-a741-922464ff03b7'),
 ('83', '203', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Collaborating with Startupbootcamp alumni WoraPay – is said to have saved Lloyds Banking Group employees 10,000 days of work. ', NULL, '2016-10-26 10:43:50', '2016-11-15 16:28:03', 'a409eeeb-e61f-4de2-a920-90677be2422e'),
 ('84', '204', 'en_us', 'New Ways of Working', '<p>For Lloyds, collaborating with the FinTech sector also provides inspiring examples of agility and working practices that refresh Lloyd’s thinking and approach to delivering digital services.</p>\n\n<p>The partnership gave Lloyds the chance to be involved in dedicated events such as FinTech Lounges and hackathons, presenting another opportunity to experience new ways of working.</p>', 'grey', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-26 10:43:50', '2016-11-15 16:28:03', '1abd96dc-abdd-436d-9c13-77293210faa3'),
